var book = {
	"name": "2 Sansiarnak",
	"numChapters": 36,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> David ih fapa Solomon in Israel ram a uknak cu a hnget deuhdeuh; Bawipa a Pathian in a thlawsuah ih mi maksak ngaingai ah a tuah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Solomon in a ralbawi ralkap thawngkhat hotu le zakhat hotu pawl hmuahhmuah, innsang ih hotu pawl, acozah bawi upa pawl le a ra khawmmi misenpi pawl cu,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Gibeon ih Pathian biaknak hmun feh dingah thu a pek. Pathian siahhlawh Moses in hramlak ramṭhing an feh laiih a rak sakmi Bawipa ih Puanthlam umnak Gibeon ahcun an zatein an feh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Thukam Kuang cu David in Kiriath Jearim ihsin Jerusalem ah a lak zo ruangah Jerusalem khua ih Puanthlam a sakmi sungah a um.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hur fapa Uri ih fapa Bezalel ih tuahmi dar biakṭheng khal Gibeon ah Bawipa Puanthlam hmaiah a um. Cutawkah Solomon le misenpi cun Pathian an biak.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Puanthlam hmaiih ummi dar biakṭheng parah thawinak pe in Solomon cun Bawipa a biak; rannung thawngkhat a that ih biakṭheng parah cun mei-ur thawinak ah a pek.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cuih zanah Pathian cu Solomon hnenah a lang ih, “Ziang so ka lo pek ding? Na duhmi i dil aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cutikah Solomon in, “Ka pa David parah duhdawtnak tumpi na rak nei ringring ih atu-ah a ai-ah siangpahrang i ṭuanter.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Maw Bawipa Pathian, ka pa ih hnenih na thukammi hmuahhmuah cu kimter aw; ziangahtile siarcawk lo minung tlunah siangpahrang ah i tuah zo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Minung hizat ka uk theinak dingah ka ṭul bikmi fimnak le theihnak i pe hram aw. Culo cun na minung hitluk tam hi ziangtinso ka uk thei ding?” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule Bawipa in Solomon hnenah, “A dikmi na hril a si. Lennak le sumsaw, a si lole hminthannak maw, na ral pawl thihnak maw, a si lole nangmah ih hrangah nun khawsaunak maw, dil loin ka minung pawl uktu siangpahrang ah ka lo tuah ih anmah uk theinak ah fimnak le theihnak i dil ruangah,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> i dil vekin fimnak le theihnak ka lo pe ding. Cuih hlei ah zovek siangpahrang hmanih an rak neih dah lomi le an neih dah lo dingmi lennak, sumsaw le hminthannak ka lo pe ding,” a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule Solomon cu Pathian biaknak hmun, Puanthlam thianghlim umnak Gibeon ihsin Jerusalem ah a kir ih Israel ram cu a uk.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Rang le rangleng tampi neih a tum ih rangleng thawngkhat le zali, le rang ralkap hrangah rang thawng hleihnih a nei. A hrekkhat cu Jerusalem khawsungah a ret ih a hrekkhat cu khawpi dangdang ah a ret.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Israel ram a uk sungah sui le ngun cu Jerusalem khawsungah lungto zat in a tam ih sidar thingkung cu theipi kung zat in a tam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Siangpahrang hrang thilri leitu pawl in Izipt le Kue ihsin rang pawl cu an lei ih,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> rangleng khal Izipt in an lei. Rangleeng pakhat cu ngun tangka zaruk in an lei ih, rang pakhat cu ngun tangka za le sawmnga an lei. Rang le rangleng an leimi pawl cu Hit siangpahrang le Siria siangpahrang hrang hnen khalah an zorh hai ṭheu."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Solomon in Bawipa ih Biakinn sak ding le amah ih hrang siangpahrang inn pakhat sak dingah a relcat ih a tawlrel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Inn saknak thing nawltu dingah minung thawng sawm sarih a lak ih lungto sertu dingah minung thawng sawm riat a lak. An hnaṭuannak zoh le hotu dingah minung thawng thum le zaruk a ret.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Solomon in ṭai-ar siangpahrang Hiram hnenah hiti in thu a cah: “Ka pa siangpahrang David na rak bawm ih a siangpahrang inn saknak ah sidar thing na rak pek bangin kei khal i bawm ve dingah zaangfah ka lo dil a si.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bawipa ka Pathian hminthannak ah biakinn pakhat sak ka tum. Bawipa ka Pathian hminthannak le upatnak ah keimah le ka milai pawl, zingtin zantin Sabbath ni le Thla Thar puai caan le a dang ni thianghlim ni ah mei-ur thawinak kan peknak hmun a si pei ih cat loin Bawipa hnenih sang thianghlim kan hunnak hmun le rimhmui a phunphun ur in Bawipa kan biaknak hmun a si ding. A kumkhua hiti ih tuah dingin Bawipa in Israel mi hnenah thu a pek zomi a si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kan Pathian cu khawzing dangdang hnakin a maksak ih a lian bikmi a si ruangah a tum ngaingai mi Biakinn pakhat sak ka tum hrimhrim a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Asinain van tumzet le kauzetmi hmanah a tlem lomi Pathian a si ruangah Pathian umnak hrangah ti ngaingai cun zohman in Biakinn kan sak thei lo ding. Pathian hnenih rimhmui urnak biakinn fang dah ti lo cu kei in ziangso ka sak thei ding?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Curuangah ka pa David in a hrilcia mi Judah ramsung le Jerusalem khua ih zungthiam pawl thawn hnaṭuan tlang dingah mi pakhat, lung ṭelhthiam, sui le ngun, dar le thir serthiam, mepian puan, puan sendup le puan sen pawl tah thiamtu i run kuat hram aw.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na minung pawl thing-ah an thiamzia tla ka theih ruangah Lebanon in sidar thing, mirang far thing le hual thing pawl i run kuat hram aw. Biakinn ka sak tummi cu a tumzet le a mawizetmi a si ding ruangah,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> thing-ah tam ngaingai ka ṭul ih na minung pawl in in rak tawlrel sak hai sehla anmah bawmtu dingah ka minung pawl tla ka hun thlah ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na minung pawl ih ei dingah sangvut haan thawng zakhat, barli sangvut haan thawng zakhat, sabitti lang thawng zali le thawng sawmli, le olif hriak lang thawng zali le thawng sawmli ka lo kuat ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule ṭai-ar siangpahrang Hiram in Solomon hnenah a thucahmi ca in a run khirh. A ca sungah cun, “Bawipa  in a minung pawl a duhdawt ruangah an siangpahrang ah a lo tuah zo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Lei le van tuahtu Bawipa Israel ih Pathian cu thangṭhat si ko seh. Amah in siangpahrang David hnenah fimnak le theihnak in a khatmi Bawipa ih hrangah Biakinn le amah ih hrangah siangpahrang inn sak a tumtu fapa pakhat a pek a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Atu-ah mifimzet le kutzung thiam ngaingaimi Huram ka run thlah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> A nu cu Dan hrin a si ih a pa cu ṭai-ar khuami a si. Huram cu sui, ngun, dar, thir, lung le thing in ziang hmuahhmuah a serthiamtu a si. Puan mepian, puan sendup, puan sen le puan phangfem tla a tah thei thluh. A ṭelh a phunphun a tuah thiam ih a ruangrai nan sim hnuhnu cu tuah thiam lomi a nei lo. Na pa siangpahrang David hnaṭuantu pawl le na hnaṭuan zungthiam pawl thawn ṭuan tlang hai seh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule kuat dingih in tiammi sangvut, barli sangvut, sabitti le olif hriak pawl cu in hun kuat aw.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Lebanon tlang ah na ṭulzat in sidar thing pawl cu kan hau ding ih pakhat le pakhat ṭemcih in puumpher ah kan tuah pei ih Joppa tiang tifinriat par in kan run kuat ding. Cutawk ihsin Jerusalem ah nang in na rak thiar pei,” tiah a ngan.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon in Israel ram sungih ummi ram dangmi pawl kha, a pa David ih a rak tuah vekin mipum siarnak a tuah. An zatein ram dangmi pawl cu thawng za le sawmnga le thawngthum le zaruk an um.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cuih sungin thawng sawmsarih cu zanthing nawltu ah, thawng sawmriat cu tlang parih lungto laitu le sertu ah a tuah hai ih a dang thawngthum le zaruk cu hnaṭuantu zoh le hotu ah a ret."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon cun Bawipa ih Biakinn cu Jerusalem khua, a pa siangpahrang David hnenih Bawipa a langnak Moriah Tlangmual ah sak a thok. Cuih hmun cu Jebus mi Araunah in a fang ciilnak puum ih a rak hmanmi a si ih David in a rak simsial thluh zo mi a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Solomon siangpahrang a ṭuannak kum li le thla hnihnak ah Biakinn sak cu a thok.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon ih a sakmi Biakinn cu pi sawmkua a sau ih pi sawmthum a kau.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Biakinn hmai ih hulhliap cu Biakinn tia in pi sawmthum a kau ih pi za le sawmriat a sang. Cuih hulhliap a phar sunglam cu sui in an khuut.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A laifang khaan cu sidar thing in an ṭelh ih sui in an khuut ih tuumkung le cikcin zuk an cuanter.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Siangpahrang in Biakinn cu lungmankhung le Parvaim ram ihsin lei mi sui in a ceimawi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Biakinn phar pawl, innbo le luanglu pawl, le sangka pawl cu sui in a khuut. A phar ah zungthiam pawl in cherubim lem pawl an cuanter.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A sungta bik khaan cu Hmun Thianghlim Bik an timi a si ih pi sawmthum a sau ih Biakinn tia in pi sawmthum a kau. Hmun Thianghlim Bik phar pawl khuutnakah sui pawng thawng sawmli le thawng nga an hmang;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> tlawngkhen an hmanmi cu sui in an tuah ih tlawngkhen hrangah sui pawng khat lenglo a rit. Tlunta khaan phar pawl tla sui hlir in an khuut.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Siangpahrang in a hnaṭuantu pawl cu thir in cherubim lem pahnih a tuahter ih Hmun Thianghlim Bik ahcun a ret.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cuih cherubim lem pawl cu sangka lam hoi in a ret hai ih artlang in an dinter. Cherubim pakhat in thla pahnih a nei ih a thla pakhat cu pi sarih le a hrek a sau; cuhrangah an thla an pharh tikah a khaan laifangah an thla cu a tong-aw ih khatlam thla in phar an dai veve; cuticun a khaan kauh lam pi sawmthum cu an thla in a dai ṭheh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Puanzar pakhat an tuah ih cuih puanzar cu pat phangfemte ih tah mi le mepian, sendup le a sen in buhmi a si; cuih puanzar cu cherubim lem pawl cuangin an ṭelhmi a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Siangpahrang in pi sawmnga le pi hnih a saangmi dar ṭhuam pahnih a tuah ih Biakinn hmaiah a phun. Ṭhuam ih lubo cu pi sarih le a hrek veve a sang.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ṭhuam ziik cu ṭhi kual a peh-aw thluhmi le dar ih tuahmi taleti zakhat in an ceimawi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ṭhuam pahnih cu Biakinn vung luhnak saklam le thlanglam ah an phun; thlanglamta cu Jakhin an ti ih saklamta cu Boaz  an ti."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon in dar in biakṭheng pakhat a tuah; pi sawmthum a sau, pi sawmthum a kau ih pi hleinga a sang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule dar in pi sarih le hrek a thuk ih a kaa a puum mi maihum tumpi a tuah; khatlam tlang ihsin khatlam tlang cu pi hleinga a si ih a kimvel cu sawmli le pi nga a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> A tlang ih lenglam kimvel ah thuaita le tlunta ti in mawiternak tlar hnih in an tuah. An mawiternak cu cawcang zuk cuang in an ṭelh ih maihum thawn peh aw in buurmi a si.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Tidai khawlnak maihumpi cu dar hlir in tuah mi cawcang lem hleihnih parah an ret ih, saklam thlanglam, nisuah lam le nitlak lam ah cawcang pathum fingfing an hoiter. Cawcang ih tawlam cu a laifang ah an tong-aw thluh zik.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Maihum phar cu pi thum a sah; a tlangzim cu khuat tlangzim vek, a si lole pangpar a par laimi vekin lenglam ah pharh nawn in a um. Cuih maihum cu tidai pung thawnghnih lenglo a tlem.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule kanto pahra tla an tuah ih panga cu Biakinn thlanglam ah, a dang panga cu Biakinn saklam ah an ret. Cuih kanto tidai cu mei-ur thawinak ih pekmi sa pawl kholhnakah an hmang. Maihum tumpi sungih tidai cu puithiam pawl in kholh awknak ah an hmang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> An tuah ṭheumi ruangrai vekin sui meivannak pahra le cabuai pahra an tuah ih Biakinn a laifang khaanpi sungah an ret; saklam ah meivannak panga le cabuai panga, thlanglam ah meivannak panga le cabuai panga an ret. Cuih hlei ah suikheng zakhat an tuah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> A sunglam tual le a lenglam tual an tuah ih a sunglam tual cu puithiam pawl hrangah a si. A sunglam le a lenglam tual karlakih kotka kharnak sangka pawl cu dar hlir in an tuam.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Maihumpi cu Biakinn nisuahnak lam thlanglam kilah an ret.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cun Huram in beel pawl, cawhleek pawl le kheng pawl a tuah, Siangpahrang Solomon hnenah tuah dingih a tiammi Biakinn thilri hmuahhmuah cu a tuah ṭheh: ṭhuam pahnih, ṭhuam parih retmi kheng ruangrai in ṭhuambo pahnih, ṭhuambo parih ṭhi kual peh-awmi pawl, ṭhuambo velkim ih a tlun le a hnuai ti ih retmi dar in tuahmi taleti zali, Cawleng pahra, Kanto pahra, Maihum, Maihum a hun dotu cawcang hleihnih, Bel pawl, cawhleek pawl le haiṭeek pawl an si. Zungthiam Huram in hi thilri pawl cu siangpahrang Solomon thupeknak bangtuk in Bawipa ih Biakinn sungih hman dingah hnawt tleumi dar in a tuah ṭheh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Siangpahrang in Jordan Phairawn, Sukkoth le Zeredah karlakih a ummi dar sodennak hmunah a tuahter ṭheh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> An tuahmi thilri a tamtuk hrangah an hmanmi dar ziangzat a rit ti cu zohman ih tuat theih a si lo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon in Biakinn sung hman dingmi thilri pawl cu kimtein a tuahter ṭheh. Ruangrai um cia vekin sui biakṭheng, Bawipa hrangih hunmi sang retnak cabuai pawl,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> meivannak ṭhuam pawl le Hmun Thianghlim Bik hmaiih van dingmi sui ṭha bikih tuahmi mei-inn pawl;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Biakinn mawiternak pangpar pawl, mei-inn pawl, sui ṭha bikih tuahmi caiceh pawl;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> mei-inn meica cehnak pawl, kheng pawl, rimhmui urnak kheng pawl le meivam kennak kheng pawl an si. An zatein sui hlirih tuahmi an si. Biakinn lenglam sangka pawl le Hmun Thianghlim Bik ih luhnak sangka pawl cu sui ih khuutmi an si ṭheh."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon in Biakinn sak a ṭheh tikah a pa David in Bawipa hnenih a rak pekmi thilri-sui, ngun le a dang thilri pawl cu biakinn thilri retnak khaan sungah a ret thluh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cuih hnuah siangpahrang Solomon in Israel miphun, hrin dangdang ih lubik le hotu pawl cu David Khawpi Zion ihsin Bawipa ih Thukam Kuang cu la tahrat in Biakinn sungih ret dingah Jerusalem ah a kokhawm ṭheh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> An zatein thla sarihnak Puai caanah an tongkhawm-aw.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> An hotu pawl hmuahhmuah an tonkhawm awk tikah Levi mi pawl in Thukam Kuang cu an zawn ih,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Biakinn ah an fehpi. Puithiam le Levi mi pawl in Thukam Kuang, Puanthlam le a thilri hmuahhmuah cu Biakinn ah an ṭhawn thluh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon le Israel mi hmuahhmuah cu Thukam Kuang hmaiah an pum aw ih tuu le caw siarcawk lo an that ih thawinak ah an pek.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule puithiam pawl in Thukam Kuang cu an zawn ih Biakinn sungah an luhpi hnuah Hmun Thianghlim Bik hmun, cherubim pahnih thla hnuai ah an ret.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cherubim thla pharhmi cun Kuang le a zawnnak fung pawl cu a khuh thluh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cuih fungzim pawl cu Hmun Thianghlim Bik hmaizawn lawngin a lang thei; hmun dang cun hmuh a theih lo. Cuih fung pawl cu atu khalah an um lai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Thukam Kuang sungah cun thil dang zianghman a um lo; Israel mi pawl Izipt ram in an suak ih anmah thawn Bawipa in thukamnak a rak tuah lai ih Moses in Sinai Tlang parah cuih Kuang sungih a rak retmi lungtlep pahnih lawng a um.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A pawl a pawl in a ṭhen-awmi puithiam hmuahhmuah an zatein, zo pawl ti um cuang loin thianhlimnak an tuah ṭheh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule Levi mi hla saktu pawl-Asaf, Heman, Jeduthun le an sungkhat hmuahhmuah, an zatein pat phangfem ih tahmi puan mankhung an sin ih biakṭheng in nisuahnak lamah darsumsel, ṭingṭang le tingrisit pawl thawn an ding; an hnenah puithiam za le kul an um ih an zatein tawtawrawt an tum.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hla saktu pawl le tawtawrawt tumtu pawl in an aw rualzet in, tawtawrawt, darsumsel pawl le tummi awnmawi dangdang thawn Pathian an thangṭhat ih: “Bawipa  cu a ṭha, In duhdawtnak cu kumkhua in a hmun,” tiah an sak. Puithiam pawl Biakinn in an suah vete in, hmakhatte-ah Biakinn cu Bawipa ih sunlawinak in mero bangin a tuam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tleunak in a khat ṭheh ih Bawipa biak khal an peh thei nawn lo."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cule Solomon in thla a cam ih: “Bawipa, mero le khawdur sungah ka um ding na ti;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Asinain na hrangah Biakinn mawizet ka sak zo, Bawipa kumkhua na umnak hrangah,” tiah a ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Israel mi hmuahhmuah cutawkah an ding. Siangpahrang cu anmah lam a hoi ih an hrangah Pathian thlawsuah a dil.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Solomon cun, “Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian cu thangṭhat si ko seh. Ka pa David hnenah thukamnak a tuah ih,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ‘Ka minung pawl Izipt ram in ka suahter ni thokin tuihsun tiang, Israel ramsung khuitawk khawpi hmanah keimah in biaknak ah tiah biakinn saknak hmun ka hril lo ih ka minung Israel hotu ding khalah zohman ka hril hrih lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sikhalsehla atu ahcun keimah in biaknak hmunah Jerusalem ka hril ih ka minung pawl uktu dingah David nangmah ka lo hril a si,’ a rak timi hmuahhmuah cu a kimter thluh zo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Ka pa in Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian biaknak ah biakinn sak a rak tum;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> asinain Bawipa in, ‘Biakinn sak na thinlung in na tummi cu thil ṭhazet a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sikhalsehla nangmah cun na sak lo pei. Na fapa, nangmah ih sungsuak na fapa in ka biakinn cu a sak ding,’ a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Atu-ah Bawipa in cuih a thutiammi cu a kimter zo. Ka pa ih ai-ah keimah Israel siangpahrang ka cang ih, Bawipa Israel ih Pathian biaknak ah Biakinn cu ka sak ṭheh zo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule Biakinn sungah Bawipa in Israel mi thawn thukamnak a tuah ih cuih thukam ngannak lungtlep pawl umnak Thukam Kuang cu ka ret zo,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cun misenpi hmuhah Solomon cu a feh ih biakṭheng hmaiah a ding ih baan phar in thla a cam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Solomon in donhleisang pakhat dar in a tuah ih tual laifangah a ret. Cuih donhleisang cu pi riat sau, pi riat kau a si ih pi nga a sang. Cuih donhleisang parah cun a kai ih misenpi hmuh ah a khuk a bil ih a kut vanlam phar in thla a cam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Maw Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian, lei le vanah nangmah bangtuk Pathian dang an um lo. Na thupekmi thinlung takte ih an thlun tikah cun na minung pawl parah na thukamnak na kimter ih na duhdawtnak na langter.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka pa David hnenih na thutiam cu na fekter ih tuihsun ahhin pakhat hman hrelh loin a kim ṭheh a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Curuangah maw Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian, ka pa bangin na Daan an thlun ih na thu ṭhatein an ngai a si ahcun a tesinfa pakhatkhatión Israel siangpahrang an ṭuan ringring pei, tiih ka pa hnenih na thutiam mi tla kimter hram aw.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na siahhlawh David hnenih na tiam mi hmuahhmuah cu maw Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian, pakhat hman hrelh loin kimter hram aw.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Asinain maw Pathian, leilung minung lakah na um thei taktak pei maw? Van ih van sin hmanah na tlem lo ruangah kei ih ka sakmi Biakinn ahhin ziangtinso na tlem ding?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Sikhalsehla Bawipa ka Pathian, kei na siahhlawh ih thlacamnak le ka lo ngennak hi i run theihsak hram aw. Na hnenih ka dilmi le ka aunak hi i ngai hram aw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hi Biakinn hi a sun a zan in in kilsak hram aw. ‘In biaknak hmun a si ding,’ na tinak hih Biakinn lam hoi in thla ka cam tikah i theihsak hram aw.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hi Biakinn hoi in ka thlacamnak le na minung Israel mi thlacamnak in theihsak hram aw. Na umnak vancung in in run thei awla kan sualnak in ngaithiam hram aw.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Mi pakhat in midang parah thil tisual mi a nei ti in sual an puh ih a sual lonak kha siatcam ih thukamnak tuah dingah hi Biakinn na biakṭheng hmai an thlenpi tikah,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> maw Bawipa, vancung in run thei awla na minung pawl ih thu cu run relsak aw. A mawhmi cu a mawhnak vekin hrem awla a sual lotu cu run luatter aw.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Na parih an sual ruangah na minung Israel pawl cu an ral pawl in an neh ih sualsir-aw in ngaithiamnak dil in hi Biakinn ah thla an ra cam tikah,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> van in run thei hram aw. Na minung pawl ih sualnak cu ngaithiam in an hnen le an pupa hnenih na pekmi ramah cun hruai kir hram aw.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Na minung pawl na parih an sual ruangah vanruah na surter lo ih sualsir aw ih hi Biakinn hoi in thla an cam tikah,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> maw Bawipa, vancung in run thei awla Israel mi na minung pawl ih sualnak cu ngaithiam hram aw. A dikmi tuah dingah nangmah in zirh hai awla, na minung pawl hnenih kumkhua an ta si dingin na pekmi hi ramah hin vanruah surter hram aw.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Hi ram sungah paam maw, natsia maw a thleng, a si lole an rawl thlisia in maw, kharbok in maw a siatsuah ṭheh; a si lole na minung pawl an ral in an do tikah le tlangrai in an nat thluh tikah,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> an thlacamnak run theihsak hram aw. Na minung Israel mi burpi in siseh, pakhatkhat in siseh, thinpit vansaang in hi Biakinn lam hoi in thla an cam tikah,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> run theihsak hram aw. Vancung na umnak in run thei awla an sualnak run ngaithiam aw. Minung ih thinlung le ruahnak cu nangmah lawng in na thei. An tuahmi ciar zoh in an thu run rel awla,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> cuticun kan pupa hnenih na rak pekmi ramih an um sung hmuahhmuah ah na minung pawl in an lo ṭihzah ding ih na thu an lo ngai ding a si.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Israel mi a si lo miphun dang pakhatkhat lam hlapi ih a ummi asinain na huham le na cahnak le na thil titheizia a theih ruangah a ra ih, hih Biakinn hoi in thla a cam tikah,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> a thlacamnak cu run theihsak hram aw. Vancung na umnak ihsin run thei awla a lo dilmi cu tuahsak hram aw; cuticun na minung Israel mi in an lo theih ih an lo ṭihzah vekin, leilungtlun milai hmuahhmuah in an lo thei ding ih an lo ṭihzah ding. Cule hi ka sakmi Biakinn hi nangmah biaknak ding hmun a si, ti an thei ding.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Na minung pawl cu raldo dingah thu na pek ih an fehnak hmun kipah hi na hrilmi khawpi le na hrangih ka sak mi Biakinn lam hoi in na hnenih thla an cam tikah,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> an thlacamnak cu run thei hram aw. Vancung in run thei awla nehnak run pek hai aw.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Na minung pawl cu na parah an sual thluh, zohman misual lo an um lo; na thinheng in an ral pawl na nehter ih an ral pawl in an kai ih ram hlapi-ah an hruai tikah,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> na minung pawl ih thlacamnak cu thei hram aw. An saltaannak ramah an siir aw ih na hnenah thlacam in an sualnak le an ṭhatlonak an phuan ahcun, maw Bawipa an thlacamnak run theihsak hram aw.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Cutawk ram in thinlung taktein le thungaithlak in an sual siir aw in kan pupa hnenih na pekmi hi ram le na hrilmi hi khawpi le na hrangih ka sak mi hi Biakinn lam hoi in na hnenah thla an cam a si ahcun,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> an thlacamnak cu run theihsak hram aw. Na umnak vancung ihsin run thei in zaangfah hai awla an sualnak tla cu ngaithiam hram aw.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> “Maw ka Pathian, atu-ah na mit in in run hmu awla hitawk hmun ih ka thlacamnak hi na hna in run ngai hram aw.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Bawipa Pathian, atu-ah tho in na cahnak langtertu Thukam Kuang thawn Biakinn sungah lut awla kumkhua in umta hram aw. Puithiam pawl an hnaṭuannak tinkim ah thlawsuahnak pe in an parih na ṭhatnak ruangah na minung pawl cu lungawi aipuang ringring in um hai seh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bawipa Pathian, hriak na culh zomi siangpahrang hi hnong hram hlah aw. Na siahhlawh David hnenih na duhdawtnak cu thei ringring hram aw,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Solomon cu thla a cam thluh tikah van in meisa a rung ih an thilpekmi thawinak pawl cu a kaang ṭheh; cule Bawipa ih sunlawinak huham in Biakinn cu a khat ṭheh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Biakinn cu tleunak in a khah ruangah puithiam pawl a sungah an lut thei lo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Van in meisa a rungmi le Biakinn cu tleunak in a khah kha Israel mi pawl in an hmuh tikah an dinnak tual ahcun an lu an kun ih Pathian bia in amah cu an thangṭhat, “Bawipa  cu a ṭha, A duhdawtnak cu kumkhua in a hmun” tiah an ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cuih hnuah Siangpahrang Solomon le misenpi in Bawipa ih hnenah thawinak an pek.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cuih thawinak hrangah Solomon in caw thawngkul hluanhnih le tuu thawng zakhat le thawngkul a pek. Cuticun siangpahrang le misenpi in Biakinn cu Bawipa ih hnenah an hlan.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Puithiam pawl cu an hnaṭuannak hmun ciarah an ding ih Levi mi pawl cu an lam hoi in an ding. Siangpahrang David ih a rak hmanmi awn-mawi a phunphun thawn, “A duhdawtnak cu kumkhua in a hmun,” timi hla sak phah in Bawipa cu an thangṭhat. Puithiam pawl in tawtawrawt an tum laiah misenpi pawl cu an ding thluh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule Solomon in a tual laifang, Biakinn hmaizawn cu a thianhlimter hnuah cutawkah mei-ur thawinak, thlairawl thawinak, le remnak thawinak pawl pekmi ih sathau cu Pathian hnenah a hlan. Hizat thawinak hrangah cun dar biakṭheng a tuahmi cu a fatet tuk ruangah cutawkah thawinak pawl a pek a si.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Solomon le Israel mi pawl in Puai cu ni sarih sung an tuah. Puai hmun ih a rami pawl cu an tam ngaingai; saklam ah Hamath khua luhnak tlangkawn in le thlanglam ah Izipt ramri tiangin an ra.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> A netnak ni ah puai an tuah. Biakṭheng hlannak ah ni sarih an rei ih puai tuahnak ah a dang ni sarih an rei lala.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Thla sarih thla, ni kul hluanthum ni ah Solomon in misenpi cu an inn ciarah a tlunter thluh. Bawipa in Israel mi le David le Solomon hnenah thluasuah a pek ruangah misenpi cu lungawi aipuang tein an tlung.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon in Biakinn le siangpahrang inn cu a saduhthah le a ruangrai suaimi sungih a um vekin tlamtlingte in a sak ṭheh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule Bawipa cu Solomon hnenah zanah a lang ih a hnenah, “Na thlacamnak ka thei ih hi Biakinn cu ka hnenih thawinak nan peknak hmun dingah ka lungkim mi a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Vanruah ka surter lo tikah maw, rawl ei ṭhehtu dingah kharbok ka thlah tikah maw, a si lole ka minung pawl parih natsia ka thlenter tikah maw,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ka hmin in kawhmi ka minung pawl in ka hnenah lungsiir in thla an cam ih ka mithmai an hawl ih an thil ṭha lo tuahnak ihsin an kirsal a si ahcun van in an thlacamnak ka thei ding ih an sualnak ka ngaithiam ding ih an ram cu ka damter ding.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hi hmun cu ka kilveng ding ih hitawk ihsin ka hnenih thla an camnak cu ka thei ding.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hi Biakinn cu ka hril zomi a si ih a kumkhua ih keimah biaknak hmunah ka thianhlimter zo mi a si. Hi hmun cu ka kilveng ding ih a kumkhua in ka humhim ding a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nangmah ih cungcang thu ahcun na pa David bangtuk in ka daan le ka thupekmi pawl na thlun ih rinsantlak le felzetin ka hna na ṭuan ahcun,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na tesinfa in Israel cu an uk ringring ding, tiah na pa David hnenih thukamnak ka rak tuahmi cu ka kimter ding.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Sikhalsehla nangmah le na minung pawl in ka daan le ka thupekmi pawl nan thlun lo ih khawzing dangdang tla nan biak asile,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ka lo pekmi ram ihsin ka lo dawihlo hai dingih keimah in biaknak hmunah tiih ka thianhlimter ciami Biakinn cu ka taanta ding; Israel cu mi hmuahhmuah ih hmuhsuammi le nautatmi ah a cang ding.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Atu ahcun hi Biakinn cu mikip ih porhmi a si; asinain cutikah cun a siatral thluh ding ih mi sukso pawl in an hmuh tikah mangbang khawruahhar in, ‘Ziangah so Bawipa in hi ram le hi Biakinn cu hiti lawmmam in a tisiat?’ an ti tikah,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> mikip in, ‘Bawipa an Pathian, Izipt ram ihsin an pupa a hruaisuaktu cu an dungtun, an hnong ih khawzing dang hmaiah an kuun ih an biaksan ruangah Bawipa in an parah hi tlukin siatsuahnak a thlenternak a si,’ an ti ding,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Solomon in Biakinn le a siangpahrang inn a sak ih kum kul a rei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Siangpahrang Hiram in a pekmi khawpi pawl tla a dinsal ih cuih khawpi sungah cun Israel mi pawl a umter.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hamath le Zobah ram tla a lak ih,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> nelrawn ih ummi Jadmor khawpi tla ralhruang in a kulh ṭheh. Hamath ramih khawpi pawl tla a din sal thluh ih rawl retnak hmunah a tuah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Solomon ih din salmi khawpi pawl cu: Beth Horon Sakta le Beth Horon Thlangta, an pahnih in ralhruang ih kulhmi an si ih an kotka pawl cu khar ih hren theihmi an si,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Baalath khawpi, rawl a retnak khawpi hmuahhmuah le a rang le a rangleng pawl a retnak khawpi pawl an si. Jerusalem khua le Lebanon le a ukmi ram sungah inn sak dingih a tummi hmuahhmuah cu a duh vekin a saksuak ṭheh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Israel mi pawl in Kanaan ram an lak laiah an thah lomi Kanaan mi pawl ih tesinfa pawl cu a hnaṭuantu an si. Hranhram in hna a ṭuanter mi pawl cu Hit mi, Amor mi, Periz mi, Hiv mi le Jebus mi an si ih an tesinfa pawl cu tuihsan tiangin sal an si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Israel mi pawl cu sal vekin hna a ṭuanter mi pakhat hman an um lo. Annih cu a ralkap pawl, a kuthnuai bawi pawl, rangleng ralkap le rangleng ralkap hotu pawl an si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Inn sak hnaṭuantu pawl zohtu dingah siangpahrang Solomon kuthnuai ah hotu bawi zahnih le sawmnga an um.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Solomon in a nupi, Izipt siangpahrang ih fanu cu David khawpi timi Jerusalem khawhlun ihsin a hrangih sakmi inn ah a ṭhawnter. Solomon cun, “Ka nupi cu Israel siangpahrang David ih inn ahcun um ding a si lo, ziangahtile Thukam Kuang a thlennak poh cu hmunthianghlim a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule Solomon in Biakinn hmaiih a dawlmi biakṭheng ahcun Bawipa ih hnenah thawinak a pek.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Moses Daan sungih a um vekin puai ni tinte in mei-ur thawinak a pe ringring. Cuih puai pawl cu Sabbath ni, Thla Thar Puai kum tinte tuah mi Thilnu Tello Sang Puai, Thlaithar Puai le Puanthlam Puai an si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> A pa David in thlun ding daan pawl a rak tuah zo vekin puithiam pawl le hlasaknak thawn puithiam pawl a bawmtu Levi mi pawl cu nitinte ih an hnaṭuan dingmi a ngaihtuah sak cia ṭheh. Cuvek thotho in Pathian ih minung David thupek bangtuk in Biakinn kiltu pawl khal cu kotka an hnaṭuannak hmun ciarah nitin an ṭuan dingmi an tuahsak cia ṭheh a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> David in thilri retnak inn pawl thuhla ah puithiam le Levi mi pawl a cahtami vekin ziang hmuahhmuah cu an tuah ṭheh a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Solomon ih tumtahmi hmuahhmuah cu a kim ṭheh. Bawipa ih Biakinn sak hram an thawh ni in an ṭheh tiang, an hnaṭuannak hmuahhmuah tlamtling lomi zianghman a um lo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cule Solomon cu Edom ram, Agaba Tipi kapih khawpi pahnih Eziongeber le Elath ah a feh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Siangpahrang Hiram in tangphawlawng pawl a run kuat ih, tangphawlawng uktu bawi pawl le a mawng ṭhangtu minung pawl thawn a run kuat. Solomon kuthnuai ih bawi pawl thawn Ofir ramah an feh tlang ih Solomon hrangah sui pawng thawngthum an rak phur."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Sheba ram siangpahrang bawinu in siangpahrang Solomon hmin thannak a thei ih thusuhnak harzetzet thawn hniksak dingah Jerusalem ah a ra. Mi tampi in an thlun ih rimhmui, lungmankhung le sui tampi phurtu kalauk pawl thawn an ra. Solomon a ton tikah a thinlung ih a ruahmi thusuhnak hmuahhmuah cu a sut ṭheh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A thusuhmi cu Solomon in a let ṭheh, a leh thei lomi pakhat hman a um lo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cutiin Sheba siangpahrang bawinu in Solomon fimzia cu a hmu ih siangpahrang innpi a sakmi,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> a cabuai parih a rawl ei ding an hunmi pawl, a kuthnuai bawi pawl ih inn pawl, siangpahrang zungih hnaṭuantu pawl an uk awkzia le an thilthuam pawl, a rawl ei tikih a zohtu hnen-um pawl le a tlanleen tikih a kiltu pawl le an hnipuan hruk daan pawl le Bawipa ih Biakinn ih thawinak a pekmi pawl hmuahhmuah a hmuh tikah cun a mang a bangtuk ih a thinlung a hlo ṭheh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cuih hnuah siangpahrang bawinu in Solomon hnenah cun, “Ka ram ihsin na thil titheizia le na fimnak thuhla ka theihmi cu a dik a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Keimah rori ra in ka mit ih ka ra lo hmuh hlanah cun in simmi cu ka zum thei lo. Ka hna lawngin ka rak theihmi cu na fimnak ngaingai ih hrek hman a rak si lo. An lo rel hnakin na fim sawn a si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na minung pawl le na kuthnuai ih hnaṭuantu pawl cu ziangtluk mi vanneiso an si! Ni tinte in na fimnak ṭongkam an thei ringring.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bawipa na Pathian cu thangṭhat si ko seh. Na parah Bawipa cu a lung a awi ih amah ih hmin in mi uktu hrimhrim si dingah siangpahrang ah a lo tuah a sihi! Amah ih minung Israel pawl cu a duhdawt ruangah le kumkhua in a humhim duh ruangah nangmah cu an parih thudik le dingthluk lairelnak thawn uktu si dingah siangpahrang ah a lo tuah a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Siangpahrang bawinu in siangpahrang Solomon cu laksawng ah sui pawng thawngkua, rimhmui tampi le lungmankhung pawl a pek. Sheba ram siangpahrang bawinu in siangpahrang Solomon hnenih a pekmi rimhmui bangtuk rimhmui ṭha cu khui hmanah a um dah lo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Siangpahrang Hiram le siangpahrang Solomon tla ih milai pawl, Ofir ihsin sui a rak phurtu pawl in hual thing le lungmankhung pawl tla an rak phur.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Solomon in cuih thing cu Biakinn le siangpahrang innih kailawn pawl tuahnak ah le hla saktu pawl ih ṭingṭang le tingrisit pawl tuahnak ah a hmang. Judah ramah cubangtuk cu an hmu dah lo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Solomon in laksawng a ngahmi pawl ai-ah Sheba siangpahrang bawinu hnenah laksawng tampi a pek ih a ngahmi hnakin tam sawn a pek. Siangpahrang bawinu ih a dilmi hmuahhmuah a pek ṭheh a si. Cuih hnuah a thluntu pawl thawn Sheba ram ahcun an kir sal.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kum tinte siangpahrang Solomon in sui pawng thawng sawm nga zikte a ngah ringring.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Himi cu sumtuahtu le dawrtuahtu pawl ih pekmi ngunkhuai tlunah a ngahmi a si. Arabia ram siangpahrang pawl le Israel ram sungih mi-uk bawi pawl in sui le ngun tampi an pek fawn.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Solomon in ralphaw a tummi zahnih a tuah ih ralphaw pakhat cu deenmi sui pawng hleinga ciarih khuhmi a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cuih tlunah a fate deuhmi ralphaw zathum a tuah ih pakhat cu deenmi sui pawng riat ciarih khuhmi a si. Cuih ralphaw pawl cu a zatein Lebanon Tupi thingih sakmi siangpahrang innkhaan pakhat sungah a ret.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Solomon in siangpahrang tokham tumpi pakhat vuiho in a tuah ih sui hlir in a khuut.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cuih tokham kainak dingah kaarbak paruk a um ih a hmai ahcun sui ih tuammi ke retnak a um. Vorhlam le kehlam ah kut retnak a um ih a siir ah kiosa lem pakhat veve an dinter.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Karbak paruk ih siir le siir ah kiosa lem hleihnih an ding. Hi bangtuk siangpahrang tokham cu khui ram hmanah a um dah lo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon ih khuathai hmuahhmuah cu sui hlir ih tuahmi an si ih Lebanon Tupi Khaan sungih beelkheng pawl tla sui hlir ih tuahmi an si ṭheh. Solomon sanah ngun cu sunloihmi a rak si lo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cule tangphawlawng tampi a nei ih siangpahrang Hiram ih tangphawlawng thawn Tarshish khua ah an fehter ṭheu. A feh le a kir ah kum thum an rei. Cuih a tangphawlawng pawl cun sui, ngun, vuiho, zawng le utawng pawl an phur.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon cu leilung tlun siangpahrang hmuahhmuah lakah a fimbik le a lianbik a si.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Pathian ih a pekmi fimnak theih duh ah siangpahrang hmuahhmuah in thu an ra ron ṭheu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Solomon cu laksawng a phunphun sui, ngun, korfualpi, hriamnam, rimhmui, rang le laak pawl an pek. Kum tinte cutin an pek ringring.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cun Solomon in a rang le a rangleng pawl hrangah ranginn thawngli a nei ih rang ralkap pawl ih to dingah rang thawng hleihnih a nei. A rang hrekkhat cu Jerusalem ah a ret ih hrekkhat cu khawpi dangdangah a ret.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Eufrates Tiva in Filistin ram le Izipt ramri tiang siangpahrang a ummi hmuahhmuah tlunah thuneitu bik a si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Solomon san ahcun ngun cu Jerusalem ah lungto tlukin a tam ih sidar thing cu theipi kung tlukin a tam.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Solomon in rang cu Izipt ram le ram dangdangin a lei.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Siangpahrang Solomon thuanthu dangdang cu, a thok ihsin a cemnak tiang, Profet Nathan Thuanthu Cabu  sungah le Shiloh khua Ahijah ih Thuphuan cabu  sungah le Profet Iddo Ih Hmuhmi Cabu  sungah an ngan. Cuih cabu sungah Israel siangpahrang Jeroboam pakhatnak ih thuhla khal an ngan ve.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Solomon in Israel ram pumpi cu Jerusalem khua ihsin kum sawmli sung a uk.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Solomon cu a thi ih David Khawpi, Jerusalem ah an phum. Cule a fapa Rehoboam in a ai-ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Saklam hrin Israel mi pawl Rehoboam siangpahrang cangter ding in Shekhem ih an rak feh cia ruangah Rehoboam cu Shekhem ah a feh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Nebat fapa Jeroboam cu siangpahrang Solomon ṭih ah Izipt ramah a tlan; asinain Rehoboam thu a theih tikah Izipt ram in a kirsal.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Saklam Israel mi pawl in Jeroboam cu an sawm ih an zatein hmun khatah Rehoboam hnenah cun an feh ih a hnenah,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Na pa in kan thil in ritter tuk. Kan thilrit hi na zaanter ih kan nunnuam deuh ih in tuah ding a si ahcun nangmah kan lo rian ding,” tiah an ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Rehoboam in, “Ni thum hnuah ra sal leh uh,” tiah a ti. Curuangah misenpi cu an tlung.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Siangpahrang Rehoboam cu a pa Solomon ruahnak petu upa pawl deuhdeuh hnenah a feh ih, “Hitiih in ti hi ziangtinso ka leh ding?” tiah thu a ron.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule annih in, “An parah zaangfahnak na neih ih ṭongthlum le ṭongmawi in an lung na awiter a si ahcun kumkhua an lo rian ko ding,” an ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sikhalsehla cuih ruahnak cu a pom lo ih, amah ih hrihruai a tlanleenpi ṭheumi mino pawl an ruahnak theih a duh ih cupawl hnenah,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Ziangtin so ka ti ding? An thilrit zaanter dingih i fialtu pawl hnenah ziangtinso thu ka leh ding?” tiah thu a ron.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cutikah annih cun,” ‘Ka zungte cu ka pa ih cawn hnakin a tum sawn a si.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka pa in nan phurh a ritter; kei khal in ka ritter sinsin ding. Ka pa in nuangfung in a lo vuak; kei in varngen tawpir thawn ka lo hrem hai ding,’ tiah an hnenah ti aw,” tiah an ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ni thum hnuah a tiamcia vekin, Jeroboam le misenpi pawl cu Rehoboam hnenah cun an ra.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Siangpahrang in upa pawl ruahnak pekmi cu a hnong ih mino deuh pawl ih ruahnak pekmi sawn la tahrat in,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> misenpi pawl hnenah cun, “Ka pa in nan phurh a ritter, kei khal in ka ritter sinsin ding. Ka pa in nuangfung in a lo vuak, kei in varngen tawpir thawn ka lo hrem hai ding!” tiah aw hrangzet in a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bawipa in profet Ahijah hmangin Nebat fapa Jeroboam hnenih a rak simmi kimter dingah Bawipa Pathian ih tummi a si. Curuangah siangpahrang Rehoboam in misenpi duhnak cu a thlun lo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Senpi pawl in siangpahrang in kan duhnak a thlun lo a si ti an hmuh tikah, “David le a hrin pawl kan duh lo. Kan hrangah ziangso an tuah dah? Israel mi pawl tlung uh. Rehoboam cu amahte in taal seh!” tiah siangpahrang Rehoboam cu an sawn ih an inn ah an tlung thluh. Cuticun Israel mi pawl cu raal an tho ih,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Rehoboam cu an tlansan ih Judah peng lawng uktu siangpahrang ah a cang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cule siangpahrang Rehoboam in sal pawl ih hnaṭuan hotu Adoniram cu Israel mi pawl hnenah a thlah; asinain Adoniram cu lungto in an rak deen that. Cutikah Rehoboam cu zamrangte in a rangleng a to ih Jerusalem ah a zaam.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cuih ihsi thokin tuih ni tiang saklam Israel Ram cu David ih tesinfa uknak dotu ringring ah an cang."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang Rehoboam cu Jerusalem khua a thleng ih Benjamin le Judah hrin sungin ralkap ṭha bik pawl thawng zakhat le thawng sawmriat a khawm. Saklam Israel hrin pawl cu do ih amah ih ukmi siter sal a tum.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Sikhalsehla Bawipa in,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> siangpahrang Rehoboam le Judah le Benjamin hrin pawl sim dingin profet Shemaiah a tirh ih Shemaiah in,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Bawipa  ih ṭongkam cu hiti in a si: ‘Nan unau Israel mi pawl cu do hlah uh. Nan zatein nan inn ah tlung thluh uh. Hitiih thil a cangmi cu keimah ih cantermi a si,’ a ti,” tiah a ti. Bawipa ih thupekmi cu an thlun ih Jeroboam cu do loin an ṭul sal.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Rehoboam cu Jerusalem khawpi sungah a um; cule Judah le Benjamin ram sungih ummi khawpi:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bethlehem, Etam, Tekoa,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bethzur, Soko, Adullam,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Gath, Mareshah, Zif,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Adoraim, Lakhish, Azekah,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Zorah, Aijalon le Hebron pawl cu ralhruang in a kulhter ciamco.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hi khawpi pawl cu fekzetin a kulhter ih khawtin ah hotu bawi a ret. Cule khua kipah rawl, olif hriak, sabitti,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ralphaw le feipi pawl a ret ih cuticun Judah ram le Benjamin ram cu feltein a uk.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Israel ram khuazakip in puithiam pawl le Levi mi pawl cu thlanglam ah Judah ram cu an pan ciamco.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Israel siangpahrang Jeroboam le a fapa pawl in puithiam pawl cu Bawipa ih hna an ṭuanter duh lo ruangah Levi mi pawl in an umnak le an leiram pawl cu an tlansan ih Judah ram le Jerusalem khua ah an vai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Jeroboam in khuavang biaknak le cawcang lem a tuahmi biaknak ah amah ih duhmi pawl puithiam a ret ih cupawl cun khuavang biaknak le milem biaknak hmunah puithiam hna an ṭuan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Israel hrin dangdang pawl sungin Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian biak a duh taktaktu pawl cun Levi mi pawl thawn Jerusalem ah, an pupa ih Pathian Bawipa hnenih thawinak pek duh ah an feh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Anmah pawl in Judah ram cu an hngetter sinsin ih kum thum sung cu Solomon fapa Rehoboam ṭhatein an bawm ih siangpahrang David le siangpahrang Solomon sanih an rak nun vekin an nung.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Rehoboam in Mahalath a ṭhi. Mahalath ih pa cu David fapa Jerimoth a si ih a nu cu Eliab fanu le Jesse ih tunu Abihail a si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Fapa pathum an nei ih Jeush, Shemariah le Zaham an si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cuih hnuah Absalom fanu Maakah a ṭhi ih fapa pali: Abijah, Attai, Ziza le Shelomith an nei.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Rehoboam in a zate in nupi hleiriat le nusun sawmruk a nei ih fapa kul hluanriat le fanu sawmruk a nei. A nupi le a nusun hmuahhmuah lakah Maakah a duh bik a si.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> A fapa hmuahhmuah lakah Maakah ih a hrinmi Abijah a duhdawt bik ruangah amah ai-awhtu dingah a hril.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Rehoboam in a fapa pawl cu ṭuanvo felzetin a zem ih Judah le Benjamin ramsung ralhruang kulhmi khawpi pawl ahcun a ret hai; an ei an in ding tla an duh zat in a pek ih nupi tampi a ṭhitsak hai."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Rehoboam cu a ramsung feltein a uk thei ih siangpahrang cakzet a hung si vete in a ukmi minung pawl thawn Bawipa ih Daan cu an dungtun.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Siangpahrang a ṭuan kum nganak ah Izipt siangpahrang Shishak in Jerusalem a do.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Rangleeng thawngkhat le zahnih, rang ralkap thawng sawmruk le ke ralkap siar cawk lo thawn a do. A ralkap sungah cun Libia mi, Suk mi le Ethiopia mi tla an tel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Judah ram ralhruang ih kulhmi khawpi pawl a lak ih Jerusalem khua kiang a thleng.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Shishak ṭih ah Jerusalem khawsung ah a zaammi Judah hotu pawl le siangpahrang Rehoboam hnenah profet Shemaiah cu a feh ih, “Bawipa  in ‘Keimah in dungtun ruangah Shishak kut sungah ka lo thlenter hai a si,’ a ti,” tiah a sim.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang le Judah hotu pawl cun kan sual a si ti an theih ruangah, “Bawipa  cu a dik a si,” an ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cumi cu Bawipa in a theih tikah profet Shemaiah hnenah a ṭong sal ih, “Kan sual a si, ti an theih ruangah ka siatsuah hai lo ding. Siatsuah ṭhehnak in a luat fangfang an si ding ih Shishak in a do tikah Jerusalem cun ka thinhengnak a tong lo ding.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sikhalsehla Shishak cun a neh hai dingih a kuthnuai ih an um hnuah keimah ih hnaṭuan le leilung tlun siangpahrang ih hnaṭuan a dan awkzia an theifiang ding a si,” a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Siangpahrang Shishak cu Jerusalem khawsung a thleng ngaingai ih Bawipa ih Biakinn le siangpahrang inn ih a ummi sumsaw hmuahhmuah a lak ṭheh. A lakmi lakah Siangpahrang Solomon ih tuahmi sui ralphaw pawl tla a tel ṭheh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cuih sui ralphaw pawl ai-ah Rehoboam in dar ralphaw pawl a tuah ih siangpahrang inn kotka kiltu ralkap hotu bawi pawl kutah a ret.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Siangpahrang bawipa Biakinn ih a fehtin in a kiltu pawl in ralphaw cu an keng ringring; cuih hnuah kotka kiltu pawl ih umnak inn ah an retsal ṭheu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Rehoboam cu Bawipa ih hmai ih a lung a nem ruangah Bawipa ih thinhengnak in a siatsuah thluh lo ih Judah ram cu tluangte in a feh thei sal.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Rehoboam in Judah ram cu Jerusalem khua ihsin a uk ih a cak deuhdeuh. Siangpahrang a can tikah sawmli le kum khat a ti ih Israel ram pumpi sungah Bawipa in amah biaknak hrangih a hrilmi Jerusalem khawpi ihsin kum hleisarih sung a uk. Rehoboam ih nu cu Ammon rammi Naamah a si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bawipa ih duhnak hawl a tum ṭheu lo ruangah Bawipa ih hmaiah thilsual a tuah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Rehoboam hnaṭuannak, a thok ihsin a cem tiang le a innsang ih thuanthu pawl cu Profet Shemaiah Thuanthu Cabu  le Profet Iddo Thuanthu Cabu  sungah an ngan a si. Rehoboam le Jeroboam cu cat loin an do aw ringring.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Rehoboam cu a thi ih David khawpi, Jerusalem, siangpahrang thlaan ah an phum. Cule a fapa Abijah in a ai-ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang Jeroboam in Israel ram a uknak kum hleiriat kumah Abijah cu Judah siangpahrang a cang ih,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Jerusalem ihsin kum thum sung a uk. A nu cu Gibeah khuami Uriel fanu Mikaiah a si. Abijah le Jeroboam cu an ral-aw ih an do-aw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Abijah in micak huaisen ralkap thawng zali a khawm ih Jeroboam in micak huaisen ralkap thawng zariat thawn a do.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Efraim tlangpar ramah an tong aw. Cutikah siangpahrang Abijah cu Zemaraim Tlangah a kai ih Jeroboam le Israel mi pawl cu, “Maw Jeroboam le Israel mi pawl, i ngai hnik uh!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian in David hnenah amah le a tesinfa pawl cu Israel mi hmuahhmuah tlunah siangpahrang si ringring theinak thu pe in bal theih nawn lomi thukam a rak tuah zo, ti kha nan thei lo maw si?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cubangtuk asinain Nebat ih fapa Jeroboam cun Pathian ih hrilmi siangpahrang Solomon dodal in ral a tho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cuih hnuah zianglam hmanih santlai lo mihuatsuak pawl a kokhawm ih Solomon ih fapa Rehoboam cu a tuah duh lomi thil tiangin an tuahter. Mino a si ih ram ukṭhang asilo ruangah an thu cu a el thei lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Atu-ah Bawipa in David tesinfa pawl a pekmi thuneihnak cu nan dodal. Ralkap tamzet nan nei ih Jeroboam ih tuahmi sui cawlem pawl cu nan khawzing ah nan tuah ih nan keng.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bawipa ih puithiam, Aaron tesinfa pawl le Levi mi pawl tla nan hnawhsuak ṭheh a si. An ai-ah miphun dangdang pawl ih tuah vekin nan puithiam pawl nan ret. Cawcang pakhat a si lole tuu pasarih a run keng theitu hmuahhmuah cu nan khawzing pawl ih puithiam ah nan canter hluahhlo a si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Sikhalsehla kannih cun Bawipa kan Pathian cu dungtun loin Amai’ hna kan ṭuan hrih a si. Aaron tesinfa a si mi puithiam pawl in puithiam hna an ṭuan ih Levi mi pawl in an bawm.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Zingtin le zantin Bawipa ih hnenah rimhmui an ur ih rannung tampi mei-ur thawinakah an pe. Cabuai parah a thianghlim mi sangreu an hung ih zanlam tinte sui meivannak ṭhuam parah mei an vang. Bawipa ih thupek vekin kannih cun kan tuah lai; asinain nannih cun Bawipa cu nan hnong zo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Atu ahhin Bawipa cu in hotu bik a si ih a puithiam pawl cu tawtawrawt thawn nanmah do dingih in kotu dingah an ralring ṭheh zo. Israel mi pawl, nan pupa pawl ih Pathian Bawipa cu do duh hlah uh! Nan neh cuang lo ding!” tiah a auh ciamco.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cuih sungah Jeroboam in a ralkap hrekkhat pawl cu Judah ralkap pawl dunglam ihsin rak bawhthup dingin a thlah. Cule ṭhenkhat pawl in an hmailam in do an tum.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Judah ralkap pawl cun khua an tang ih an hun zoh tikah in kulh thluh a si, ti an hmu. Cutikah Bawipa ih hnenah bomnak dilin an au ih puithiam pawl in an tawtawrawt cu an tum.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Judah ralkap pawl cu napi in an au ih Abijah ho in Israel ralkap pawl do in an nam ciamco; Pathian in Jeroboam le Israel ralkap pawl cu a neh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Israel ralkap pawl an tlan ih Pathian in Judah mi pawl hnenah nehnak a pek.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Abijah le a ralkap pawl in Israel ralkap pawl cu an neh seksek ih Israel ralkap lakih a ṭha bik pawl thawng zanga an that.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cutiin Judah mi pawl in an pupa ih Pathian Bawipa an rinsan ruangah Israel mi tlunah nehtu an si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Abijah in Jeroboam le a ralkap pawl cu a duum ih an khawpi hrekkhat: Bethel, Jeshanah le Efron le hi khawpi kiangkapih khawte pawl tla a long.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Abijah siangpahrang a si sungah Jeroboam cu a cak sal thei nawn lo. Neta bikah Bawipa in Jeroboam cu a hrem ih a thi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Asinain Abijah cu a cak deuhdeuh. Nupi hleili a nei ih fapa kul hluanhnih le fanu hleiruk a nei.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Abijah ih thuanthu dang, a thusimmi le a thil tuahmi pawl cu Profet Iddo Thuanthu Cabu  sungah an ngan a si."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang Abijah cu a thi ih David khawpi, siangpahrang thlaan ah an phum. Cule a fapa Asa in a ai-ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan. Asa ih kuthnuai ah Judah ram cu kum hra sung daihnak an ngah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Asa cun a dik le a ṭhami a tuah ruangah Pathian lung a awiter.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ramdangmi pawl ih biakṭheng pawl le an khawzing biaknak hmun pawl cu a bal thluh; an serhmi lungphun pawl a khuai ih an khawzing nu Asherah lem pawl tla a siatbal ṭheh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> An pupa pawl ih Pathian Bawipa ih duhnak tuah dingah le a zirhnak le a thupekmi pawl thlun dingah Judah mi pawl cu thu a pek hai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Judah ram khawpi hmuahhmuah ih ummi khawzing biaknak hmun le rimhmui urnak biakṭheng pawl a siatbal ṭheh ruangah a ukmi ram sungah daihnak a um.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cuih caanah Judah ram khawpi pawl cu ralhruang in a kulh ih Bawipa in daihnak a pek ruangah kum tampi sung do awknak a um lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Judah mi pawl hnenah, “Kan khawpi pawl kimvel cu ralhruang in kan kulh ṭheh pei. Khuaram thlirnak innsang pipi kan sak pei ih khar theihmi le hren theihmi kotka kan tuah pei. Pathian duhnak kan tuah ruangah kan ram cu feltein kan uk thei. Amah in khuazakip ah humhimnak in pek a si,” tiah a ti. Curuangah a tivek cun an sak ih an ṭhangso sinsin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Siangpahrang Asa in Judah mi sungin ralphaw le fei kengtu ralkap thawng zathum le Benjamin mi sungin ralphaw le conkiang neitu ralkap thawng zahnih le thawng sawmriat a nei. An zatein ralṭha zet le raldo zir cia hlir an si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ethiopia mi, Zerah an timi pa in ralkap million khat le rangleng zathum thawn Judah ram a do ih Mareshah tiang a hun nor.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Asa cu Zerah do dingah a pok ih an kap hnih in Mareshah kiang Zefathah Phairawn ah ṭanhmun an khuar veve.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutikah Asa in Bawipa a Pathian hnenah thla a cam ih, “Maw Bawipa, ralkap cak zetmi siseh, ralkap ṭawnṭai zetmi siseh, na duh ahcun olte in na bawm thei a si. Maw Bawipa kan Pathian, nangmah lawng kan lo rinsan ih na hmin in ralkap hizat tam hi do dingah kan rasuak zo a si; atu-ah in bawm hram aw. Bawipa, nangmah cu kan Pathian na si ih zohman in nangmah neh ding cu an tum ngam lo ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule Asa le Judah ralkap in an do tikah Bawipa in Ethiopia ralkap pawl cu a neh. Ethiopia ralkap pawl cu an tlan ih,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Asa le a ralkap pawl in Gerar tiang an dawi. Ethiopia ralkap pawl cu tamzet thah an si ruangah raldo thei an si nawn lo. Bawipa le a ralkap pawl in an neh hai ih ralkap pawl in hransaw tampi tla an long.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cutawk hrawngih a ummi pawl in Bawipa cu an ṭih tuk ruangah Judah ralkap pawl in Gerar kiangkapih ummi khawpi pawl cu an siatsuah ṭheh. Khawpi tamzet an ram ih hransaw tamzet an lak.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tuukhal pawl riahhmun hrekkhat pawl tla an nam ih tuu le kalauk tampi an long. Cuih hnuah Jerusalem ah an tlung."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Pathian ih thlarau cu Oded ih fapa Azariah parah a rung thleng ih,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> siangpahrang Asa hnenah a feh ih, “Siangpahrang Asa, Judah le Benjamin mi pawl, i ngaihnik uh! Bawipa lamih nan ṭan sung cu Bawipa in a lo ṭan ve a si. Amah nan hawl a si ahcun ton theih in a um ding; asinain nan dungtun a si ahcun a lo dungtun ve ding.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Israel mi pawl cu caan reipi Pathian dik nei lo, zirhtu puithiam nei lo le daan nei loin an um.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sikhalsehla harsatnak an ton tikah Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian hnenah an kir sal. Bawipa cu an hawl ih an tong ṭheu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Culai caan ah khuazakipah ṭihphannak le remlonak a um ruangah khui hmanah zohman an suakvak ngam lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Pathian in an parah harsatnak le vansaannak a thlenter ruangah ram khat le ram khat, khua khat le khua khat an rem-aw lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sikhalsehla nannih cu cakzet le ralṭha zetin nan um pei ih nan hnaṭuan man nan co ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Asa in Oded ih fapa profet Azariah ih thuphuanmi a theih tikah a tha a tho zet. Judah le Benjamin ram le Efraim tlangpar ram an lakmi khawpi hmuahhmuah sungih a ummi milem pawl cu a hlonsak ṭheh. Cule Biakinn tualih a ummi Bawipa ih biakṭheng tla a rem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Efraim ram, Manasseh ram le Simeon ram ihsin minung tampi Asa hnenah an ra ih a ram sungah an um; ziangahtile a hnenah Bawipa a um ti an hmu. Asa in cuih a rami pawl le Judah mi le Benjamin mi pawl cu a kokhawm.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Asa siangpahrang a ṭuan kum hleinga kum, thla thumnak ah Jerusalem ah an tongkhawm aw.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cuih ni ahcun an ral pawl hnenin an lonmi hransaw sungin caw zasarih le tuu thawng sarih Bawipa ih hnenah thawinakah an pek.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> An pupa ih Pathian Bawipa cu an thinlung le an thazaang zate thawn bia dingah an zate lungkim in thukam an tuah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Zozo khal, mino siseh, upa siseh, nunau mipa tilo in, Bawipa a bia lotu cu thah si dingin thu an kam-aw.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bawipa ih hmin in cuih an thukam cu thlun dingah ringzet in siat an cam ih tawtawrawt le tuucangki tum in napi in an au ciamco.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> An thinlung taktein thukam an tuah ruangah Judah mi hmuahhmuah cu an lung a awi ngaingai. Pathian an biaknak parah lunghmuinak an nei. Pathian ih pommi miphun ah an cang ih khuazakip ah daihnak a pek.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cun siangpahrang Asa ih pi Maakah in khawzingnu Asherah lem a tuah ruangah siangpahrang bawinu ih nu a sinak in Asa in a hlon a si. Asa in milem cu a hauthluk ih a tan seksek hnuah Kidron Horkuam ah meisa in a ur.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Asa cun Israel ram sungih khawhrum biaknak hmun hmuahhmuah cu a siatbal thluh lo naón a damsung hmuahhmuah ah Bawipa rinsan in a nung.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Pathian hnenah a pa Abijah ih pekmi thilri pawl le amah ih pek mi sui le ngun in tuahmi bungbeel pawl cu Bawipa ih Biakinn sungah a ret ṭheh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Judah ram a uknak kum sawmthum le kum nga sung cu a ram sungah do awknak a um lo."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang Asa ih Judah ram a uknak kum sawmthum le kum ruknak ah Israel siangpahrang Baasha in Judah ram cu a do ih, Judah ramsung suah luhnak kham thluh dingah Ramah khawpi ralhruang in a kulh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cutikah Asa in Bawipa ih Biakinn le siangpahrang inn ih an retmi sui le ngun pawl cu a lak ih Damaskas ah Siria siangpahrang Benhadad hnenah a kuat. Cuih tlunah,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Kan pa le pawl ṭangkhat an rak si vekin kannih khal kan ṭangkhat pei. Hi sui le ngun hi laksawngah ka lo ṭhen a si. Israel siangpahrang Baasha in a ram sung ihsin a ralkap pawl kirpi dingah amah thawn nan ṭantlangnak cu phiat thlang aw,” tiah thu a cah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Benhadad in Asa ih thucahmi cu a lungkim ih Israel khawpi pawl do dingah a ralbawi pawl le an homi ralkap pawl a thlah. Israel cu an do ih Ijon, Dan, Abel Beth Maakah le Naftali ramih rawl an retnak khawpi pawl an lak ṭheh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cuih thu cu Baasha in a theih tikah Ramah ralhruang kulhnak tuah nawn loin a tlansan.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule siangpahrang Asa in Judah ramsung hmunkip in milai a khawm ih Baasha in Ramah kulhnak ih a hmanmi lungto le zanthing pawl cu a phurhter hai ih Geba le Mizpah khawpi kulhnakah an hmang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Culai ah profet Hanani cu Judah siangpahrang Asa hnenah a feh ih, “Bawipa  na Pathian rinsan lo in Siria siangpahrang na rinsan sawn ruangah Israel ralkap pawl cu na kut sung ihsin an luat thluh zo a si.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ethiopia le Libia ralkap pawl cu rangleng le rang ralkap an nei tam deuh ngaingai a si lo maw? Cutluk tam an si naón Bawipa na rak rinsan ruangah Bawipa in nehnak a lo pek a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bawipa cun Amah rinsannak thinlung a neitu hnenah thazaang cak pe dingin leilung pumpi hi a zoh ringring a si. Aatthlakzet ih thil na tuah zo ruangah atu thokin ral na do ringring ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cumi thu a theih tikah Asa cu profet Hanani parah a thin a heng ngaingai ih thawngah a thlak ih thir cikcin in a hren. Cuih caan hrawngah Asa in a ramsungmi hrekkhat pawl cu zaangfahnak nei loin a hrem hai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Asa ih Judah ram a uk sung thil a cangmi hmuahhmuah cu a hramthokin a net tiang, Judah Le Israel Siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu  sungah an ngan a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Asa cu Judah siangpahrang a ṭuannak kum sawmthum le kum kua kumah a ke ah besia zetin hma sia a tuar. Asinain Pathian rinsan loin sibawi pawl a rinsan sawn.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Siangpahrang a ṭuannak kum sawmli le kum khat kumah a thi ih,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> David khawpi ah amah hrangih a rak kherciami lung thlaan ah an phum. A ruak phumnak ah rimhmui le siti rimthaw pawl an hmang ih amah upatnak ah meipi nasa zetin an tik."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Asa a thih tikah a fapa Jehoshafat in a ai-ah Judah siangpahrang a run ṭuan ih Israel do dingah a tha a cakter sinsin.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A ralkap pawl cu Judah khawpi tampi ah le hramlakah le Asa in Efraim ram a lakmi khawpi sung tla ah a ret vivo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> A pa no laiih nunzia thlun in Baal khawzing a biak lo ruangah Bawipa in Jehoshafat cu thlawsuah a pek.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Jehoshafat cun a pa ih biakmi Pathian rian in a thupekmi vekin a thlun ih Israel siangpahrang dang pawl vekin thil ṭha lo a tuah lo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bawipa in amah cu Judah ram feltein a ukter ih mi hmuahhmuah in a parah lungawi in laksawng an pek ciamco ruangah milianzet le upat ṭihzah zetmi ah a cang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bawipa ih hnaṭuan a uar zet ih Judah ram sungih khawhrum biaknak hmun pawl le Asherah lem pawl khal a siatbal ṭheh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Judah siangpahrang a ṭuan kum thumnak ah a tanglam ih bawi pawl: Benhail, Obadiah, Zekhariah, Nethanel, le Mikaiah cu Judah ram khua pawl sungih mi zirhtu dingah a thlah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A tlunih bawi pawl cu Levi mi pakua: Shemaiah, Nethaniah, Zebadiah, Asahel, Shemiramoth, Jehonathan, Adonijah, Tobijah, Tobadonijah le puithiam pahnih Elishama le Jehoram in an thlun.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bawipa ih Daan cabu an keng ih Judah ram khua hmuahhmuah ah an feh ih misenpi an zirh vivo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bawipa ih huham ruangah Judah ram kiangkap ih a ummi ram hmuahhmuah in Jehoshafat do ding cu an ngam lo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Filistin mi hrekkhat pawl in Jehoshafat cu laksawng tampi an pek ih ngunkhuai ah ngun tampi tla an pe. Arab mi pawl khal in tuu thawng sarih le zasarih le me thawng sarih le zasarih an pe.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cuticun Jehoshafat cu a ṭhangso deuhdeuh ih a cak deuhdeuh fawn. Judah ram sungah rawl le thilri khawlnak khua pawl a tuah ih ralhruang in a kulh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cuih a dinmi khua pawl ahcun thilri tampi a ret. Jerusalem khua ah ralbawi le ralkap ṭha bik pawl",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> a hrin a hrin in a ret. Judah hrin sungin Adnah cu ralkap hotu bawi a si ih a kuthnuai ah ralkap thawng zathum an um.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Pahnihnak cu Jehohanan a si ih a kuthnuai ah ralkap thawng zahnih le thawng sawmriat an um.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Pathumnak cu Zikhri ih fapa Amasiah a si ih ralkap thawng zahnih a nei. Amasiah cu pum pe-aw in Bawipa ih hnaṭuantu a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Benjamin hrin sungin ralkap hotu bawi cu ralkap hminthangzet Eliada a si ih ralphaw le conkiang hriamnam kengtu ralkap thawng zahnih hotu a si.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Eliada sangtu bawi cu Jehozabad a si ih hriamnam kimzet thawn ralkap thawng zakhat le thawng sawmriat a nei.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hi ralkap pawl cu Judah ram khawpi pawl ih a retmi ralkap pawl hlei ah Jerusalem ih siangpahrang riantu an si."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Judah siangpahrang Jehoshafat cu milianzet le mi hminthangzet a hung can tikah a sungkhat hrekkhat pawl le Israel siangpahrang Ahab ih sungkhat pawl thawn ṭhit-umnak in pehtlaih awknak a tawlrel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cuih hnu kum reipi hnuah Jehoshafat cu Ahab tlawng dingin Samaria khua ah a feh. Jehoshafat le a thluntu pawl upatnak ah Ahab in puai tumpi a tuah ih caw le tuu tampi a thah. Cule Ahab in Gilead ramih Ramoth khua do dingah Jehoshafat cu a sawm.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ahab in, “Ramoth ka do ding ih na tel thei ve pei maw?” tiah a ti. Jehoshafat in, “Ka lo ṭanpi ding. Na man tikah i sim awla kei le ka ralkap pawl kan pok ding.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Asinain hmaisabik ah Bawipa kan ron ta pei,” tiah a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Curuangah Ahab in profet zali tluk a ko ih, “Ramoth ka do ding maw, do lo dingso?” tiah a sut hai. Profet pawl cun, “Do aw. Pathian in nehnak a lo pe ding,” an ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sikhalsehla Jehoshafat in, “Bawipa  kan ron theinak dingah Bawipa ih profet pakhat tal an um lo maw?” tiah a sut.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cutikah Ahab in, “A dang pakhat a um hrih. Imlah fapa Mikaiah a si. Asinain Mikaiah cu ka hua; ziangahtile ziangtik hmanah ka hrangah thuṭha a phuang dah lo; a simmi cu thuṭha lo a si ringring,” tiah a ti. Jehoshafat cun, “Cuvek ṭong cu siangpahrang na hmurka in suakter hram hlah aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Curuangah siangpahrang Ahab in a kuthnuai bawi pakhat a ko ih Mikaiah zamrangih ko dingah a fial.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule Ahab le Jehoshafat cu an siangpahrang thuam in an thuam-aw ih Samaria khawpi kotka leng fangrialnak hmunah siangpahrang tokham veve ah an to ih an hmaiah cun profet pawl cu profet ṭong in thu an sim rero.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Profet pawl lakah pakhat Khenaanah ih fapa Zedekiah in thir in tuuki pawl a tuah ih Ahab hnenah, “Bawipa  in, ‘Hi bangtuk ki pawl thawn Siria mi nan do ding ih nan neh ding,’ a ti,” tiah a sim.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Profet dang khal in cubangtuk in an sim ciar. “Ramoth do dingah feh awla na neh mai ding. Bawipa in nehnak a lo pe ding a si,” an ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cu sungah Mikaiah kawh an fialmi pa cun Mikaiah hnenah, “Profet dang hmuahhmuah in siangpahrang ih neh dingah an sim ciar. Nang khal an sim vekin na sim le a ṭha ding,” a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Asinain Mikaiah cun, “Bawipa  ih hmin saal in ka lo sim: Ka Bawipa ih i simtermi lawnglawng ka sim ding,” tiah a sawn.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Mikaiah cu Ahab siangpahrang hmai ih a thlen tikah siangpahrang in, “Mikaiah, siangpahrang Jehoshafat le keimah in Ramoth kan do ding maw, do lo ding, i sim aw?” tiah a ti. Cutikah Mikaiah in, “Do hnik hmen uh! Nan neh meen ding! Bawipa in nehnak a lo pe ko ding,” tiah a sawn.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cutikah Ahab in, “Bawipa  ih hmin in ka hnenih na ṭong tikah thudik na ṭong pei tiah voi ziangzatso ka lo sim ding?” tiah a ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule Mikaiah cun, “Israel ralkap pawl cu fing le tlangpar ah khaaltu nei lo tuu pawl bangin suk le so ah an vakvai ka hmu. Cule Bawipa in, ‘Himi pawl cu hotu an nei lo; daitein an inn ah tlung hai seh,’ a ti,” tiah a sim.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cutikah Ahab in Jehoshafat hnenah, “Hi pa cun ka hrangah thuṭha a sim dah lo, ka lo ti tho lo maw? Ziangtik khalah thusia ringring a sim,” tiah a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cule Mikaiah cun, “Bawipa  ih ṭong cu ngai hrih uh. Bawipa cu a vancungmi pawl in a kimvel in an kil ih vancung a bawi tokham parih a to khi ka hmu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bawipa in, ‘Ahab cu Ramoth ah feh tahrat in thah tong ding ah zo in so a vung buum ding? tiah a suh tikah vancungmi hrekkhat in phunkhat an sim; a dang in phundang an sim.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cutikah thlarau pakhat cu hmaiah a ra suak ih Bawipa cu a rak naih ih, ‘Keimah in ka vung buum ding,’ tiah a ti. Bawipa in, ‘Ziangtin so na buum ding?’ tiih a suh tikah,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> cuih thlarau cun, ‘Ka vung feh pei ih Ahab ih profet hmuahhmuah thuphan ka perter thluh ding,’ tiah a sawn. Bawipa in, ‘Feh awla vung buum aw. Na buum suak thei ding,’ a ti,” tiah a sim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cule Mikaiah in, “Cuvek cekci in a cang ngaingai a si. Bawipa in na profet pawl hmuahhmuah cu na hnenah thuphan a relter ṭheh hai. Sikhalsehla Bawipa Amah in vanduainak na tonnak dingah lai a rel zomi a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cutikah profet Zedekiah cu Mikaiah hnenah a hung feh ih Mikaiah cu a biang ah a beng ih, “Ziangtik in so Bawipa thlarau in i tlansan ih na hnenah thu a lo sim?” tiah a sut.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Mikaiah cun, “A thuuk bik khaan sungih na relh tikah na thei leh ko ding,” tiah a sawn.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cule siangpahrang Ahab in a kuthnuai bawi pakhat hnenah, “Mikaiah hi kai awla khawpi uktu bawi Amon le siangpahrang fapa Joash hnenah hei hruai aw.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Himdamteih ka ra thlen sal hlanlo thawng ah rak thla hai sehla thawngtla rawl, tidai le sang rak pe ve hai seh,” tiah a fial.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cutikah Mikaiah in, “Himdamteih na rakir sal thei a si ahcun Bawipa in ka hnenah a ṭong lo a si ding. Ka sim mi hi mi hmuahhmuah in thei hai seh,” tiah ringzet in a au.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cun Israel siangpahrang Ahab le Judah siangpahrang Jehoshafat cu Gilead ramih Ramoth khawpi do dingah an feh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cule Ahab in Jehoshafat hnenah, “Ral kan do tikah nang cu na siangpahrang thuam hruk awla kei cu mi meenmeen vekin ka thuam-aw ding,” tiah a ti. Cuticun Israel siangpahrang cu midang vekin tuah-aw tahrat in ral a do.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Siria siangpahrang in a rangleng ralkap hotu bawi pawl cu Israel siangpahrang bawipa siar lo midang zohman tuahmawh lo dingin thu a pek.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cule siangpahrang Jehoshafat an hmuh tikah Israel siangpahrang ah an ruat ih an nam ciamco. Asinain Jehoshafat cu a au ih Bawipa Pathian in a run ih a hualtu pawl cu an kir.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Rangleeng ralkap hotu bawi pawl in Israel siangpahrang a si lo kha an theih tikah an dawi nawn lo.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Asinain Siria ralkap pakhat pa in bah-mi nei cuca loin a conkiang a hei sai ih siangpahrang Ahab cu a awmphaw le ralthuam peh awknak a hliah zawnte-ah a hei ngah. Cutikah Ahab cu, “In ngah ee!” tiah a au ih a rangleng mawngtupa cu raldonak hmun ihsin tlanpi dingah thu a pek.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Cuih ni an do-awk cu a nasa ngaingai ih Ahab cu a rangleng parah do cop in Siria ralkap pawl lam hoi in a zau ih nitlak zawng ah a thi."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Judah siangpahrang Jehoshafat cu himdam tein Jerusalem khua a inn ah a kir sal.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule Hanani ih fapa profet Jehu cu siangpahrang Jehoshafat tong dingah a feh ih a hnenah, “Mi ṭha lo pawl bom le Bawipa a huatu pawl hnenih ṭan hi a ṭha tiah na ruat maw si? Hitiih na tuah ruangah nangmah ih parah Bawipa ih thinhengnak na thlenter.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Asinain na ṭhatnak khal cu a um ve: midang ih an biakmi khawzingnu Asherah lem pawl na hlon ṭheh ih Bawipa ih duhnak na hawl ringring,” tiin nun a sim.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Jehoshafat cu Jerusalem khawpi ah a um naón Judah a ram sungah thlangta bik Beersheba in sakta bik Efraim tlangpar ramri tiang khual a tlawng ringring ih a minung pawl cu an pupa ih Pathian Bawipa hnenih hoikir sal dingah a forh vivo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Judah ram sungih khawpi kipah thuṭhentu pawl a ret ih,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> an hnenah, “Thu nan rel ih thuṭhennak nan tuah tikah ralringzet in nan tuah pei; thu nan ṭhen tikah nanmah ih thuneihnak in thu nan ṭhen a si lo; Bawipa ih thuneihnak in a si; cule thu nan ṭhen tikah Amah cu nan lakah a um a si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bawipa ṭihzah uhla ralringzet in hna ṭuan uh; ziangahtile Bawipa in mibum, mi thleidan le nawhthuh ei pawl a zawi thei hrimhrim lo,” tiah thu a cahta vivo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Jerusalem khua khalah siangpahrang Jehoshafat in thuṭhentu ah Levi mi, puithiam pawl le khawsung upa hminthang pawl a ret hai ih Bawipa ih daan an buar tikah le khawsungmi taza an cuai-awk tikah thuṭhentu an si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> An hnenah, “Nan ṭuanvo cu Bawipa ṭihzah phah in felte le thleidannak nei lotein nan ṭuan pei.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Khua dangdang ihsin nan unau pawl, pakhat le pakhat an thah pang awknak thu-ah siseh, Bawipa ih daan le thupekmi an buarnak thu-ah siseh, nan hnenih an thlen tikah Bawipa parih sualnak an neih lonak dingah ralringzet in an ṭuanvo ciar cu nan simfel pei. Cumi nan tuah lo a si ahcun nanmah le nan unau pawl in Bawipa ih thinhengnak nasa zetin nan tuar ding. Sikhalsehla feltein nan ṭuanvo nan tuah a si ahcun mawh nan phur lo ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Biaknak lam thu hmuahhmuah ah puithiam sang Amariah cu thuneitu bik a si ding; khawsungmi pawl ih thu ahcun Judah ram uktu bawi Ishmael ih fapa Zebadiah thuneitu bik a si ding. Thuṭhentu pawl ih thuṭhenmi tuahsuak dingah ṭuanvo a neitu cu Levi mi pawl an si ding. Ralṭhazet in ṭuan uhla hi ka lo cahmi thu bangin tuah uh; Bawipa cu midik pawl parah um hram seh,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tikcu a hung rei tikah Moab ralkap le Ammon ralkap pawl in, anmah ṭantu Meunim mi pawl thawn Judah ram an do.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Siangpahrang Jehoshafat hnenah thuphurtu an ra thleng ih, “Edom ram in ralkap tam ngaingai an ra ih Tipi Thi khatlam ral in a lo do an tum a si. Hazazon Tamar khua tla an la zo,” tiah an sim. (Hazazon Tamar cu En-gedi ti khal in an ko.)",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Jehoshafat cu a thin a phang ih thlacam in Bawipa ih hruainak a dil. Cule a ramsungmi hmuahhmuah rawl ul dingah thu a pek.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Judah ram khawkip in Jerusalem ah Bawipa ih hruainak dil dingin an ra.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Jerusalem khuasungmi pawl thawn Biakinn tual thar ah an tongaw khawm. Siangpahrang Jehoshafat cu an hmaiah a va ding ih,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ring zetin thla a cam: “Maw Bawipa, kan pu le kan pa ih Pathian, na umnak van ihsin leitlun miphun hmuahhmuah nangmah in na uk ṭheh. Cahnak le huham hmuahhmuah nangmah ih ta an si ih a lo dodal theitu zohman an um lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nangmah cu kan Pathian na si. Na mi Israel pawl hitawk ram an ra thlen tikah hitawk ih a rak ummi miphun pawl cu na dawi hai ih na rualpa Abraham ih tesinfa pawl hnenah hi ram cu kumkhua an ta si dingin na pek.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hi ram sungah an um ih nangmah upatnak ah Biakinn an sak.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Harsat vansaannak a phunphun-raldo siatsuahnak, natsia le paam an hnenih a thlen tikah hi Biakinn hmaiah ding in an lo bia, an lo ngennak hmun ah an tuahmi a si. Na hnenih thla an ra cam tikah na theih sak ih na run hai ṭheu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Maw Bawipa, atu-ah Ammon mi, Moab mi le Edom mi pawl in in do. Kan pupa pawl Izipt ram ihsin an rak suah laiah hi ram pawl hi an pal phah ding na rak siang lo; curuangah kan pupa pawl in an ram cu an heel ih an siatsuah lo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cucingin atu-ah in thungrulh tum daan hi zohhnik-in pekcia mi ram ihsin a dawihlo in tum a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Maw Pathian, kan Pathian, Nangmah in hrem hai aw. In dotu ralkap hizat hmaiah cun kan caang thei hrimhrim lo. Ziang hman kan tuah theimi a um nawn lo; nangmah ih bom ding lawng kan hngak a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Judah mi hmuahhmuah an nupi le an faate pawl thawn Biakinn tual ahcun an ding.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bawipa ih thlarau cu misenpi lakih a ummi Levi mipa pakhat hnenah a rung thleng. Amah cu Jahaziel a si ih Zekhariah ih fapa, a si. Zekhariah cu Benaiah ih fapa a si; Benaiah cu Jeiel ih fapa a si; Jeiel cu Mattaniah ih fapa a si; Mattaniah cu Levi miphun Asaf hrin a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule Jahaziel cun, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa le Judah ram mi le Jerusalem khuami pawl, Bawipa in, ‘Nan ral pawl an tam ruangah phang hlah uh, nan thin tla nau hlah seh. Raldonak cu nan thu a si lo, Pathian lairel a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Thaisun ah nan do pei. Ziz tlangkawn in an ra ding ih Jeruel kiang phairawn a netnak, hramlak a thoknak zawn ah nan tong hai ding.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nannih in nan do a ṭul lo ding. Ṭanhmun khuar uhla tiarcia in um uh; cule Bawipa in nehnak a lo pek kha nan hmu ding. Judah le Jerusalem mi pawl, ṭih hrimhrim hlah uh; nan thin khal nau hlah seh. Ral do dingah feh uhla Bawipa Keimah nan hnenah ka um ding,’ a ti,” tiah a sim.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang Jehoshafat cu a hmai leilung dai tiangin a kun, misenpi khal an kun ih Bawipa cu an biak.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Levi phun Kohath le Korah hrin pawl an hung ding ih ring zetin Israel ih Pathian Bawipa cu an thangṭhat.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> A thaizing zingpitte in an tho ih Tekoa kiang hramlak lamah cun an feh. An pawh zawng ah Jehoshafat in an hnenah, “Judah le Jerusalem mi pawl, Bawipa nan Pathian cu rinsan uhla hnget zetin nan ding thei ding. Amah ih profet pawl thusimmi zum uhla nan hlawhtling ding,” tiah a cah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Misenpi pawl thu a ron hnuah hla saktu hrekkhat pawl cu puai caanih an hruk ṭheumi korfualpi hruk ih ralkap hmaiah feh tahrat in: “Bawipa  cu thangṭhat uh, In duhdawtnak cu kumkhua in a hmun,” tiah hlasak phah dingah thu a pek.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hla saktu pawl in Bawipa thangṭhatnak hla an sak vete in Bawipa in Judah ram a dotu ral pawl cu nasa zetin an lung a phanter.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cutikah Ammon mi le Moab mi an ṭangtlang ih Edom ralkap pawl kha an ṭhuat ciammam ih Edom ralkap pawl cu an that ṭheh. Cuih hnuah anmah le anmah nasa zetin an do aw lala.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Judah ralkap pawl cu tlangbo an thlen tikah an hei zoh ih an ral pawl cu lei parah ril teptep in an hmu. Pakhat hman luat loin an thi thluh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Jehoshafat le a ralkap pawl cu an ral pawl ih thilri la dingin an va feh. Caw, rawl, hnipuan le thil mankhung a phunphun tampi an hmu. Cuih thilri hransaw pawl cu ni thum sung an thiar rero naón an thiar cawk lo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ni linak ah Berakah Phairawn ah an khawm-aw ih Pathian an thangṭhat. Cuih phairawn cu atu tiangin Berakah tiah an ko tata.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bawipa in an ral pawl a nehter hnuah Jehoshafat le a ralkap cu Jerusalem ah ralneh lungawinak thawn an kir sal.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Jerusalem an thlen tikah ṭingṭang le phirivau le tawtawrawt tum phah in Biakinn ah an feh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bawipa in Israel ih ral pawl a nehsak ṭheh ti a rak theitu ram hmuahhmuah cu an thin a phang thluh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bawipa in a ram sung khuazakip a humhim ruangah Jehoshafat in daitein a uk.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Jehoshafat cu kum sawmthum le kum nga a ti ah Judah siangpahrang a cang ih Jerusalem in kum kul hluannga sung a uk. A nu cu Shilhi fanu Azubah a si.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> A pa Asa bangtuk in Bawipa ih hmaiah thil ṭha a tuah;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> asinain khuavang an biaknak hmun pawl cu a siatbal lo. Misenpi cun an pupa ih Pathian cu an thinlung hmuahhmuah in an bia lo a si.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Jehoshafat ih tuahmi dangdang cu, a thokin a netnak tiang, Israel Siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu  timi sungih a telmi Hanani Fapa Jehu Thuanthu Cabu  timi sungah an ngan a si.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Voikhat ah Judah siangpahrang Jehoshafat in thil ṭha lo tampi a tuahtu Israel siangpahrang Ahaziah thawn ṭantlangnak cakhen a tuah.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Eziongeber an timi tangphawlawng colhnak hmun Tarshish lam fehtu ding tangphawlawng pawl an tuah ciamco.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Asinain Mareshah khuami Dodavahu ih fapa Eliezer in Jehoshafat cu, “Ahaziah thawn nan ṭantlang ruangah na tuahmi pawl cu Bawipa in a siatsuah thluh ding,” tiah ralrinnak a pek. A sim vekin an tangphawlawng pawl cu a siat thluh ih Tarshish ahcun a feh lo."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Jehoshafat cu a thi ih Jerusalem khuahlun, David khawpi, siangpahrang thlaan ah an phum. Cule a fapa Jehoram in a ai-ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Judah siangpahrang Jehoshafat ih fapa Jehoram in unau paruk a nei: Azariah, Jehiel, Zekhariah, Azariahu, Mikhael le Shefatiah tla an si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> An pa in sui, ngun le thilri mankhung tampi a pek ih Judah ram sung ralhruang kulhmi khawpi pakhat ciarah hotu-ah a ret hai. Asinain Jehoram cu upa bik a si hrangah Jehoshafat in a ai-awhtu ah a tuah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Jehoram in Judah ram a uknak a hnget deuh tikah a unau pawl cu a that ṭheh ih Israel bawi hrekkhat pawl tla a that.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Jehoram cu kum sawmthum le kum hnih a ti ah siangpahrang a cang ih Jerusalem ihsin kum riat sung a uk.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ahab fanu pakhat a ṭhit ruangah a nunzia a ṭha lomi siangpahrang Ahab le Israel siangpahrang dang pawl ih nunzia a cawng. Cuticun Bawipa ih mithmuh ah sualnak a tuah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sikhalsehla Bawipa in David hnenah thukamnak a rak tuah ih a tesinfa pawl in ram an uk ringring ding tiah a rak tiam zo ruangah David ih thokmi ram-uknak cu Bawipa in a siatsuah siang lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Jehoram in Judah ram a uk laiah cun Edom mi pawl ral an tho ih mahte uknak an lak.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutikah Jehoram le a ralbawi pawl cu an pok ih rangleng thawn Edom ram an do. Cutawkah Edom mi pawl in an rak kulh ṭheh; asinain a thupte in zanah an suak ih an luat.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cuihsin thokin Edom ram cu mahte uk-awmi ramah a cangta. Jehoram in a pupa ih Pathian Bawipa cu a dungtun ruangah cuih caan thotho ah Libnah khuami pawl tla ral an tho ve.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Judah tlangpar ramah khuavang biaknak tiangin a sak ciamco ih cuticun Judah le Jerusalem mi pawl cu Bawipa ih hmaiah misual ah a canter a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule profet Elijah in Jehoram cu ca a kuat ih a ca sungah cun, “Na pa Jehoshafat le na pu Asa vekih na nun lo ruangah nan cithlahtu David ih Pathian Bawipa in a lo hnong a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Israel siangpahrang pawl ih nunzia na thlun ih, Ahab le amah ih ai-awhtu pawl in Israel cu lam an pialter vekin, Judah le Jerusalem mi pawl lam na pialter a si. Nangmah hnakin miṭha deuh a si mi na unau pawl na that ṭheh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Curuangah Bawipa in na minung pawl le na faate le na nupi pawl nasa zetin a hrem ding ih na neihmi thilri hmuahhmuah an hloral ṭheh ding.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nangmah cu pumnat na nei ding ih na ril a pawtsuak tiangin ni khat hnu ni khat a besia sinsin ding,” tiah a ngan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Culai ah Filistin hrekkhat le Arab mi hrekkhat pawl cu tipikap ih a um Ethiopia mi pawl kiangkap ah an rak um. Cuih pawl cu Jehoram do dingah Bawipa in a forh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Judah ram cu an do ih siangpahrang inn an ram ih a fapa nauta bik Ahaziah siar lo siangpahrang nupi pawl le a fapa hmuahhmuah an hruai ih thawngah an thlak.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cuih hnuah Bawipa in siangpahrang cu a pum a natter.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> A nat a luar deuhdeuh ih kum hnih hnuah a tuar harzet in a thi. A uk mi minung pawl in amah hlanih siangpahrang a ṭuantu pawl hrangih meipi an tih ṭheu vekin a thih tikah meipi hman an tik lo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Jehoram cu kum sawmthum le kum hnih a ti ah siangpahrang a cang ih Jerusalem in kum riat sung a uk. A thih tikah zohman an ning a hang lo. David khawpi Jerusalem khawhlun ah an phum; siangpahrang thlaan ah an phum lo."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Arab pawl in Jerusalem an do laiah mi hrekkhat in siangpahrang Jehoram fapa hmuahhmuah, a nauta bik Ahaziah siar lo, an that ṭheh. Curuangah Jerusalem mi pawl in a pa ai-awh ah Ahaziah cu siangpahrang ah an tuah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ahaziah siangpahrang a can tikah kum kul hluanhnih a ti ih Jerusalem in kum khat a uk. A nu cu Israel siangpahrang Omri ih tunu, Ahab fanu Athaliah a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> A nu in thusia a forh ruangah Ahaziah cun siangpahrang Ahab ih innsang nunzia a cawng ih thil ṭha lo a tuah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A pa thih hnuah siangpahrang Ahab innsang pawl cu siangpahrang Ahaziah ruahnak petu an si ih ruahnak ṭha lo an pek ruangah Bawipa ih parah a sual ih amah dirthlatu ah an cang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> An thu a lung ih Israel siangpahrang Joram hnenah ṭang tahrat in Siria siangpahrang Hazael an do. Gilead ram Ramoth ah an ral pawl thawn an do-aw ih Joram cu hriamhma a pu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> A hma tuamhlawm dingah Joram cu Jezreel khua ah a kir ih cutawkah Ahaziah in a veh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ahaziah in Joram a veh cu Bawipa in Ahaziah cemter dingah caan ṭha a ti. Ziangtin tile cutawkih Ahaziah a caam laiah Ahab ih a rak thokmi uknak siatsuah dingin Bawipa ih a hrilmi Nimshi, Jehu fapa, in Ahaziah le Joram a zuam hai.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Pathian ih thurel ciami a tuahsuaktu cu Jehu a si ruangah Ahaziah thluntu Judah ram hotu pawl le Ahaziah unau ih fapa pawl thawn an tong aw. Cutikah Jehu cun an zatein a that ṭheh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ahaziah cu an hawl ih Samaria khua ih a relhnak ah an kai. Jehu hnenah an hruai ih Jehu cun a rak that. Cule Bawipa ih hna a theih tawkih a ṭuan vemi a pu Jehoshafat an upat ruangah Ahaziah ruak cu ṭhatein an phum. Ahaziah sungkhat sungin ram a uk theitu ding pakhat hman an um lo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Siangpahrang Ahaziah ih nu Athaliah in a fapa an thah thu a theih vete in Judah ram siangpahrang sungkhat pawl hmuahhmuah a thatter ṭheh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ahaziah in farnuseu pakhat Jehosheba a nei ih a pasal cu puithiam Jehoiada a si. Jehosheba cun a thupte in Ahaziah fapa pakhat Joash an timi a lak; thah ding a si mi a unau dang pawl hnenin a tlanhlopi ih a kiltu ding sayama pakhat thawn Bawipa ih Biakinn ih ihnak khaan pakhat sungah a thup. Cutiih a humsuak ruangah Athaliah kutih thihnak ihsin Joash cu a luat.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Athaliah siangpahrang bawinu a ṭuan sung kum ruk sung cu cutawkah a relh ringring."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kum sarihnak ah puithiam Jehoiada cun thil pakhatkhat tuah caan a kim tiah a ruat. Curuangah ralbawi panga: Jeroham ih fapa Azariah, Jehohanan ih fapa Ishmael, Obed ih fapa Azariah, Adaiah ih fapa Maaseiah le Zikhri ih fapa Elishafat pawl thawn thutiamnak pakhat an tuah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Judah ram sung khua hmuahhmuah ah an feh ih Levi mi pawl le an hrin ciarih lubik pawl an zatein Jerusalem ah an ko ṭheh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Misenpi cu Biakinn ah an pumkhawm ih siangpahrang fapa Joash thawn thutiamnak an tuah. Cule Jehoiada in an hnenah, “In thihsantu kan siangpahrang ih fapa cu hinah a um. Bawipa in David tesinfa pawl cu siangpahrang an si ringring ding ti ih thu a rak kam cia vekin atu-ah amah cu siangpahrang a si ding.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Siangpahrang a cannak dingah hiti in kan tuah pei. Puithiam le Levi mi pawl, Sabbath ni hnaṭuan dingih nan rat tikah ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat in Biakinn kotka pawl nan kil pei;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> a dang ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat in siangpahrang inn nan kil pei; a dang ṭhenthum ṭhenkhat in Hramṭonak Kotka nan kil pei. Senpi pawl cu Biakinn tualah nan khawm-aw pei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hnaṭuan neitu puithiam le Levi mi pawl siar lo zohman Biakinn sungah nan lut lo pei. Puithiam le Levi mi pawl cu thianhlimter mi nan si ruangah nan lut thei pei; asinain midang pawl cu Bawipa ih thupekmi vekin a lengah nan um pei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Levi mi pawl cun nan ralnam zuuk cia in siangpahrang nan kil pei ih a fehnak kipah nan thlun pei. Biakinn sung luh a tumtu cu zo a si khalle nan that pei,” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Levi mi pawl le Judah misenpi pawl in Jehoiada ih thupekmi an ngai ih a sim vek cun an tuah ṭheh. Hnaṭuan a nei nawn lotu pawl khal an inn ah an tlunter lo ruangah hnaṭuan hotu bawi pawl in hnaṭuan a thok dingmi pawl siseh, a ṭheh zotu pawl siseh, ho dingah milai cat loin an nei ringring.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Puithiam Jehoiada in Biakinn sungih an ret ringring mi siangpahrang David ih feipi le ralphaw pawl cu bawi pawl hnenah a pek.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Siangpahrang humhim dingah mi tampi cu an ralnam zuuk cia in Biakinn hmailam kimvel ah a ret.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule Jehoiada in Joash cu a suahpi ih a lu ah siangpahrang lukhuh a khumter. Siangpahrang ih thlun dingmi daan cabu pi an pek ih cuticun siangpahrang ah an tuah. Puithiam Jehoiada le a fapa pawl in Joash cu hriak an culh ih mi hmuahhmuah in, “Siangpahrang a nunkhua sau hram seh!” tiah an au ciamco.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Senpi pawl in siangpahrang an thangṭhat le an cawimawi thawmvang cu Athaliah in a theih tikah misenpi an pumkhawmnak Biakinn ahcun zamrangte in a va feh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule cutawkah siangpahrang thar cu siangpahrang hrangah timi Biakinn sangka ṭhuam kiangah ralkap bawi pawl le tawtawrawt tumtu pawl in an kulh ih a din kha a hmu. Mi hmuahhmuah lungawi aipuang zetin an au ih an tawtawrawt an tum ih, hla satu pawl cu an thiltum mi pawl thawn cuih an cawimawinak ahcun mi hotu bik an si. Cutikah Athaliah cun a ninghang riahsia in a hnipuan a thlek ih, “Phiar thupnak! Phiar thupnak!” tiah a au ciamco.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Biakinn kapih Athaliah thah ding cu Jehoiada in a duh lo ruangah ralbawi pawl a thlah ih, “Ralkap pawl in a siir veve in kil hai sehla hruai hai seh; zo a si hmanah Athaliah run a tumtu cu that uh,” tiah thu a pek.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> A ti vekin an kai ih siangpahrang inn ah an hruai ih Rang Kotka timi hmunah an that.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Jehoiada ih tawlrelnak thawngin Siangpahrang Joash in misenpi pawl thawn Bawipa ih minung si dingah Bawipa ih hnenah thukamnak an tuah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cule an zatein Baal khawzing biakinn ah an feh ih an balsiat ṭheh. An biakṭheng pawl le milem pawl cu ṭok seksek in an deen ih biakṭheng hmai rori ah Baal puithiam Mattan cu an that.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cun Jehoiada in puithiam le Levi mi pawl cu Bawipa ih Biakinn ih hnaṭuantu si dingah ṭuanvo a pek. Siangpahrang David ih ṭuanvo rak zem cia vekih hnaṭuantu si dingah Moses Daan bangtuk in Bawipa hnenih an pekmi thawinak pawl cu meisa in an ur ding. Biakinn hlasak ding le lungawipuai tuahnak pawl tla anmah ih ṭuanvo a si ṭheh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Jehoiada cun Biakinn sungah raitluan lo zohman lut lo dingin khamtu ah Biakinn kotka ah kotka kiltu pawl a ret.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ralbawi pawl, bawi dangdang pawl le khawsung upa hminthang pawl in Jehoiada an thlun ih an zatein siangpahrang bawipa cu Biakinn ihsin siangpahrang inn ah an fehpi. Tlunta kotkapi in an lut ih siangpahrang bawipa cu siangpahrang tokham parah a to.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Mi hmuahhmuah lungawi aipuang in an um ih, Athaliah a thih zo ruangah khawpi sung khal cu hnahnawhnak zianghman a um nawn lo."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Joash cu kum sarih a ti in Judah siangpahrang a ṭuan ih Jerusalem in kum sawmli sung ram a uk. A nu cu Beersheba khuami Zibiah a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Puithiam Jehoiada a dam sungah cun Joash in Bawipa ih hmaiah thilṭha a tuah ih Bawipa ih lung a awiter.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Siangpahrang Joash hrangah Jehoiada in nupi pahnih a hrilsak ih fanu le fapa tampi an hrin.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Caan malte sung siangpahrang a ṭuan hnuah Joash in Bawipa ih Biakinn rem a tum.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Puithiam pawl le Levi mi pawl cu Judah ramsung khawkip ah a thlah ih kumtin Biakinn remnak hrangih a ṭulmi paisa khuan dingah thu a pek. Zamrangte ih tuah dingah a fial naón Levi mi pawl cun zamrangte in an tuah lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Curuangah an hotu Jehoiada cu a ko ih, “Bawipa  umnak Puanthlam zohnak ah senpi pawl in ngunkhuai an pek pei, tiah Bawipa ih siahhlawh Moses in thu a taanta mi cu ziangah so Judah le Jerusalem mi pawl hnen ihsin Levi mi pawl na khuanter lo?” tiah a sut.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Misual nu Athaliah le a thluntu pawl in Bawipa ih Biakinn cu tampi an siatsuah ih thilri thianghlim tampi tla Baal khawzing biaknak ah an rak hmang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang bawipa ih a fial vekin Levi mi pawl in paisa retkhawmnak ding thingkuang pakhat an tuah ih Biakinn kotka ah an ret.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Pathian siahhlawh Moses in hmaisa bik ngunkhuai cu hramlakih a rak khuan bangtuk in Bawipa hnenih ngunkhuai pe ding in Jerusalem le Judah ramsung hmuahhmuah ah thu an than.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cuih an thuthanmi an theih tikah misenpi le an hotu pawl an lung a awi ngaingai ih an ngunkhuai cu an pek ciamco ih thingkuang an tuahmi cu a khat.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nitinte in ṭuanvo neitu siangpahrang kuthnuai ih bawi pakhat hnenah cuih kuang cu Levi mi pawl in an hei phur ṭheu. Thingkuang a khat zo ti an hmuh tikah paisa cu siangpahrang bawipa ih sungṭuan le Puithiam Sang ih palai pa in an lak ih thingkuang cu an retnak keel ah an ret sal. Cuticun paisa tam ngaingai an khawl.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cun siangpahrang Joash le puithiam Jehoiada in Biakinn rem hnaṭuan hotu pawl hnenah paisa cu an pek ih annih in Biakinn remtu ah lungsertu, zungthiam le thir tuahtu pawl an lak.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hnaṭuantu hmuahhmuah in taima zetin an ṭuan ih Biakinn cu an sak pek vekin ṭhazet le fekzet in an rem thei sal.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> An rem ṭheh tikah a hleimi sui le ngun pawl cu siangpahrang bawipa le puithiam Jehoiada hnenah an khirhsal ih annih in Biakinn hrangih a ṭulmi beelkheng pawl tuahnak ah an hmang. Jehoiada a damsung cu Biakinn ah cat loin thawinak an tuah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Jehoiada cu tarkuun tiang a nung ih kum za le sawmthum a ti ah a thi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Israel misenpi hrang, Pathian hrang le Bawipa ih Biakinn hrangih thilṭha tuahtu a si ruangah Jehoiada cu David khawpi, Jerusalem khawhlun siangpahrang thlaan ah an phum.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Jehoiada a thih hnu ahcun Judah hotu pawl in siangpahrang Joash cu an forh ih anmah ih thu thlun in a nung.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Curuangah misenpi in Bawipa ih Biakinn ah an pupa ih Pathian biak nawn loin milem le Asherah khawzingnu pawl an biak. Cutiih an sual ruangah Judah le Jerusalem parah Bawipa ih thinhengnak a thleng.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bawipa in a hnenih kirsal dingah an hnenah profet pawl a thlah naón an thu an ngai duh lo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cule Pathian ih thlarau cu puithiam Jehoiada fapa Zekhariah hnenah a thleng ih misenpi in an hmuh theinak hmunah ding tahrat in an hnenah, “Bawipa  in, ‘Ziangruangah ka thukham nan thlun lo ih nan parah siatsuahnak nan thlengter?’ tiah thu a lo sut a si. Bawipa nan dungtun ruangah a lo dungtun ve,” tiah a au.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang Joash le misenpi in an phiar ih Zekhariah cu Biakinn tualah siangpahrang thupek in lung in an deng that.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Zekhariah pa Jehoiada in a rak zaangfah ih a rak kilkhawi reronak cu siangpahrang Joash in a theih nawn lo ruangah Zekhariah a that a si. Cule Zekhariah in a hnukcah zawng ah, “Nan thilti mi hi Bawipa in hmu hramsehla nan parah phu la hram seh,” tiah a au.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cuih kum ṭhal caan a hung suak ih Siria ralkap in Judah ram le Jerusalem khua an do. Judah mi hotu pawl hmuahhmuah an that ih thilri le paisa tampi an lak hnuah Damaskas khua ah an phur.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Siria ralkap cu an malte naón Judah mi pawl in an pupa ih Pathian Bawipa an dung tun ruangah Bawipa in a tamzet mi Judah ralkap pawl cu a nehter a si. Siangpahrang Joash in Bawipa ih hremnak a tong ngaingai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ral an donak ahcun besia zetin hma a pu ih, an ral pawl an kirsal hnuah, a kuthnuai ih bawi pahnih in an phiar ih puithiam Jehoiada ih fapa an thahmi phulaknak ah a ihkhun parah an that. David khawpi ah an phum ih cuticun siangpahrang thlaan ih phum hman a tong lo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Joash a phiartu cu Ammon nunau Shimeath ih fapa Zabad le Moab nunau Shimrith ih fapa Jehozabad an si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu Simfiangnak  sungah a fapa pawl ih thuanthu, amah ih hrang profet thuphuan mi pawl le Biakinn a remnak pawl cu an ngan a si. Cuih hnuah a fapa Amaziah in a ai ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Amaziah cu kum kul hluannga a ti ah siangpahrang a cang ih Jerusalem ihsin kum kul hluankua sung a uk. A nu cu Jerusalem khuami Jehoaddin a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amaziah in Bawipa ih hmaiah thilṭha a tuah ih Bawipa ih lung a awiter; asinain a thinlung zate cun a pe lo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Judah ram hngette ih a uk thei vete in a pa a rak thattu bawi pawl a that.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Asinain an faate pawl cu a that lo. “An faate pawl ih sualnak ruangah an nupa pawl nan that lo pei; cule an nupa pawl ih sualnak ruangah an faate pawl nan that lo pei. Mi pakhat cu amah in a tuahmi sualnak ruang lawnglawng ah thah ding a si,” tiah Moses Daan sungih Bawipa ih thupekmi a thlun.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule Amaziah in Judah miphun le Benjamin sungih mipa hmuahhmuah ralkap ah a lak ṭheh ih an hrin ciar in a ṭhen ih thawngkhat hotu le zakhat hotu ralbawi a ret vivo. Mipa kum kul ihsin a tlunlam hmuahhmuah a lak ih an zatein thawng zathum an si. Raldotu dingah raldo thiam cia, feipi le ralphaw hmang thiamtu an si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cuih tlunah Israel ihsin ralkap thawng zakhat a sang ih a san man ah ngun phurh zakhat a pek.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Asinain profet pakhat siangpahrang bawipa hnenah a feh ih, “Hi Israel ralkap pawl cu na hnenah tel hlah hai seh. Hi Saklam Ram ih ralkap, hi Efraim mi pawl hnenah Bawipa a um lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Anmah an tel ahcun ral do tikah ka cak deuh ding tiah na ruat ding; sikhalsehla an tel ahcun na ral in an lo neh ding, ziangahtile nehnak le sunnak cu Bawipa ih thu a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang Amaziah in, “Cuti asile ka pek ciami ngun hmuahhmuah cu ziangtinso ka tuah ding?” tiah profet cu a sut. Profet in, “Cuhnakih tam sawn Bawipa in a lo pe ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Curuangah Amaziah in a sanmi ralkap pawl cu a thlah ih an ramah a tlunter ṭheh. Israel ralkap pawl cu Judah mi pawl parah thin na zetin an tlung.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule Amaziah in ṭihnak zianghman nei nawn loin a ralkap pawl cu Cite Phairawn ah a hruai hai. Cutawkah cun an do-aw ih Edom ralkap thawng hra an that.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cuih tlunah a nungin thawng hra an kai. An kaihmi pawl cu Sela khua ih khaam zimah an hruai ih cutawkin an tulthlak thluh ih a hnuai ih lungto lakah cun an thi, an parh ṭheh a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Culai ah Amaziah in raldonak ah fehter loih a khammi Israel ralkap pawl khan Judah ram khawpi Samaria le Beth Horon karlakih a ummi pawl an do ih minung thawngthum an that ih hransaw tampi an lak.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Amaziah cu Edom ralkap a nehnak in a rakir tikah Edom milem pawl a rak phur ih a pathian ah a tuah ih a biak; cuih milem pawl hmaiah rimhmui tla a ur.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cuti a tuah ruangah Amaziah parah Bawipa cu a thin a heng ih profet pakhat a thlah. Profet cun, “Na cahnak a neh thei lo ih a milai pawl hman a humhim thei lotu ramdang ih khawzing pawl cu ziangah so na biak?” tiah siangpahrang Amaziah cu a sut.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cutikah Amaziah in, “Ziangtik in so siangpahrang ruahnak petu-ah kan lo tuah? ṭong nawn hlah; culole ka lo that ding!” a ti. Profet cu a ṭong nawn lo; asinain a baan hlanah, “Hitiin thil na tuah ih ka thusimmi tla na ngai lo ruangah nangmah siatsuah ding ah Pathian in a ruatcat zo, ti ka thei a si,” tiah a tita.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Judah siangpahrang Amaziah in Israel ram phiar a duh. Curuangah Israel siangpahrang Jehoash hnenah do awk zuamnak thu a cah. Jehoash cu Jehoahaz ih fapa a si ih Jehoahaz cu Israel siangpahrang a rak si mi Jehu ih fapa a si.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cutikah Jehoash in Amaziah cu hiti in thu a khirh: “Voikhat ah Lebanon Tlangah hlingbur pakhat in sidar thing hnenah thu a cah ih, ‘Ka fapa ih nupi dingah na fanu i pe aw,’ a ti. Cule sahrang pakhat a kiangin a ra ih hlingbur cu a pal beek thluh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Atu-ah Edom mi pawl ka neh tiah na hngal ih na puarthau zet; asinain ṭhatein ka lo sim; daitein na inn ah rak um sawn aw. Nangmah le na minung pawl hrangih siatsuahnak a si dingmi thil cu ziangah so na tawhhrawh duh rero?” a ti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sikhalsehla Amaziah in cuih thu cu a ngai duh lo. Edom mi pawl ih milem a biak ruangah Amaziah cu sung dingin Bawipa ih tumtah ciami a si.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cun Israel siangpahrang Jehoash cu Judah siangpahrang Amaziah do dingin a feh. Judah ram Beth Shemesh ah an tawng aw.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Judah ralkap pawl cu an sung ih inn lamah an tlan ṭheh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Jehoash in Amaziah cu a kai ih Jerusalem ah a hruai. Cule Jerusalem kulhnak ralhruang cu Efraim Kotka in Khawkil Kotka tiang, kaih zahnih sung a bal ṭheh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hransaw a lakmi Biakinn sui le ngun pawl, Obed Edom tefa pawl ih an kilmi Biakinn thilri pawl le siangpahrang inn ih sumsaw hmuahhmuah Samaria ah a fehpi ṭheh. Sal ih a kaihmi pawl tla a fehpi a si.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Judah siangpahrang Amaziah cu Israel siangpahrang Jehoash hnakin kum hleinga a nung rei sawn.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Amaziah ih uknak hramthok in a cem tiangih a tuahmi dangdang pawl cu Judah le Israel Siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu  sungah kimtein an ngan a si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Amaziah in Bawipa a dungtun thok ihsin Jerusalem ah Amaziah phiartu an um ringring; cu ruangah Lakhish khua ah a tlan; asinain cutawkah a phiartu pawl cun an thlun ih an that.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> A ruak cu Jerusalem ah rang in an phur ih David khawpi, siangpahrang a thlaan ah an phum."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Judah mi in Amaziah ih fapa, kum hleiruk ti, Uzziah cu a pa ai ih siangpahrang ṭuan dingah an hril.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A pa Amaziah thih hnuah Uzziah in Elath khua a la sal ih a rem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uzziah cu kum hleiruk a ti ah siangpahrang a cang ih Jerusalem ihsin kum sawmnga le kum hnih sung a uk. A nu cu Jerusalem khuami Jekoliah a si.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A pa ih nunzia thlun in Bawipa ih hmaiah thilṭha a tuah ih Bawipa ih lung a awiter.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Uzziah cu Zekhariah in Bawipa ṭihzah upat dingah a zirh ih Zekhariah a damsung ahcun Bawipa ih hna felzetin a ṭuan. Curuangah Bawipa in mal a sawm a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule Uzziah in Filistin ram a do. Gath, Jamnia le Ashdod khua pawl kulhnak ralhruang a bal ṭheh ih Ashdod kiangkap le Filistin ram hmun dangdangah ralhruang ih kulhmi khua tampi a dinter.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Pathian bomnak in Filistin mi, Gurbaal ih um Arab mi le Meun mi pawl a neh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ammon mi in Uzziah hnenah siah an pek. Uzziah cu a cakzet ih Izipt ram tiangin a hmin a thang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Uzziah in Jerusalem kulhnak ralhruang cu fek deuhdeuh in a sak ih Khawkil Kotka, Phairawn Kotka le ralhruang a kelnak zawn kipah ralvennak inn donhleisang a sak.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hramlak nelrawn khalah ralhruang ih kulh mi ralvennak innsanghlei a sak. Rannung tampi a neih ruangah nitlaknak lam tlanghram ah le hmunrawn khalah tikhur tampi a lai. Lo thlawh lam ngainami a si ruangah tlangpar ram le ram ṭhatnak hmun kipah sabit hmuan le lo tuah dingin misenpi a forh ciamco.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Raldo zir ciami ralkap tamzet a nei. Ralkap mipum cazin cu siangpahrang kuthnuai ih ralbawi pakhat Hananiah ho in siangpahrang sungṭuan pahnih Jeiel le Maaseiah in an kai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A ralkap pawl hotu-ah ralbawi thawnghnih le zaruk an um.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> An kutthuai ah ralkap thawng zathum le thawng sarih le zanga cu siangpahrang ral dotu dingah timtuah cia ringring in an um.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Uzziah in a ralkap pawl cu ralphaw, feipi, thir lukhuh, thir angki, li le conkiang pawl le lungherhden hrangah lungto tiangin a pek.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Jerusalem khua ralvennak innsanghlei le ralhruang kiil in conkiang le lungherhden saitu le lungto tumpipi sai theitu pawl ih an hman dingah hriamnam tuah thiamtu pawl in thilthuam a phunphun an tuah. Uzziah hmin cu khuazakip ah a thang; Pathian bomnak nasa zetin a ngah ruangah a cak ngaingai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Asinain siangpahrang Uzziah cu a rung cah ngaingai tikah mi hngalzet ah a cang ih cumicun a dirhthlak a si. Bawipa a Pathian a dodal ruangah Biakinn sungah feh tahratin rimhmui urnak biakṭheng ah rimhmui a ur.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Puithiam Azariah le mi cakzet le ralṭhazet puithiam sawmriat in,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> kham dingah siangpahrang cu an thlun. Puithiam pawl in, “Uzziah, nang in Bawipa ih hnenah rimhmui ur theinak thu na nei lo. Aaron tesinfa a si mi puithiam pawl lawnglawng hi hna ṭuantu dingah thianhlimtermi an si. Hi hmun thianghlim ihsin tlan aw. Bawipa Pathian cu a thin na ṭeuter ih thlawsuah a lo pe nawn lo ding a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Uzziah cu Biakinn sung rimhmui biakṭheng kiangah cun a ding ih rimhmui urnak kheng cu a kai ringring. Puithiam pawl parah a thin a heng ih cuvete in phaarnat in a cal ah a run tlak.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Azariah le puithiam dang pawl cun tuksum in siangpahrang bawipa ih cal cu cat loin an zoh ih cuih hnuah Biakinn ihsin tlan dingah an dawisuak. Cule Pathian in a hrem ruangah amah khal zamrangte in leengah a suak duh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> A nunsung hmuahhmuah a phar ruangah siangpahrang Uzziah cu mithiang lo ah a cang. Biakinn sungah a lut thei nawn lo ih a innsung lawngah a um; a hnaṭuan hmuahhmuah cu an sawng ih a fapa Jotham in ram a uk.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Siangpahrang Uzziah in ram a uk sungih hna a ṭuanmi dangdang pawl cu Amoz ih fapa Isaiah in cabu sungah a ngan thluh a si.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Uzziah cu a thi ih siangpahrang thlaanmual ah an phum; asinain a natnak ruangah siangpahrang pawl an phum ṭheunak thlan ahcun an phum lo. A fapa Jotham in a ai-ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Jotham cu kum kul hluannga a ti ah siangpahrang a cang ih Jerusalem ihsin kum hleiruk sung a uk. A nu cu Zadok fanu Jerushah a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A pa vekin Bawipa ih hmaiah thilṭha a tuah ih Bawipa ih lung a awiter; asinain a pa vek cun Biakinn sungah lut tahratin thilsual a tuah lo. Misenpi pawl in sualnak thil ṭha lo an tuah ringring.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Biakinn ih Saklam Kotka a saktu le Jerusalem khawsung Ofel veng an timi kiangih khawpi kulhnak ralhruang nasa zetih a saktu cu amah Jotham a si.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Judah ram tlangpar ah khua tampi a din ih hramlak khalah raldo ṭannak le ralvennak innsanghlei pawl a sak.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ammon siangpahrang le a ralkap pawl a do ih a neh. Cule Ammon mi cu siah kumtinten kum thum sung a hnenih pe dingah thu a pek. A thupekmi vekin kumtin an pekmi siah cu ngun pawng thawng sarih le za nga, sangvut haan thawng sawmnga le barli sangvut haan thawng sawmnga an si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bawipa a Pathian ih thu cu feltein a thlun ruangah Jotham cu siangpahrang cakzet ah a cang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Siangpahrang a can sungih thil a tuahmi, a raldonak le a thil tumtah mi dang pawl cu Israel le Judah siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu  sungah kimten an ngan a si.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Jotham cu kum kul hluannga a ti in siangpahrang a cang ih Jerusalem in kum hleiruk sung a uk.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> A thi ih David khawpi ah an phum. Cule a fapa Ahaz in a ai ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ahaz cu kum kul a ti ah siangpahrang a cang ih Jerusalem ihsin kum hleiruk sung a uk. A cithlahtu Siangpahrang David ih nunzia cu a cawng lo; Bawipa ih lungawi lonak thil sawn a tuah;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Israel siangpahrang pawl ih nunzia a thlun. Thir in Baal khawzing lem pawl a bur ih a tuah;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hinnom Phairawn ah rimhmui a ur ih, Israel mi pawl Kanaan ram an luh laiih Bawipa in a dawimi miphun pawl ih fihnungza thil tuahmi pawl a cawn ruangah a fapa pawl tiangin milem hnenih thawinak ah a pek.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Khuavang biaknak le khawhrum umnak hmun kipah le tlangpar kipah le thinghneem hnuai kipah Ahaz cun thawinak a pek ih rimhmui a ur vivo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ahaz a sual ruangah Bawipa a Pathian in Siria siangpahrang hnenah nehnak a pek ih Judah mi tampi kai in Damaskas ah thawngah an thlak. Bawipa ih bomnak thotho in Israel siangpahrang Remaliah ih fapa Pekah in Ahaz cu a neh ih ni khat ah Judah ralkap ralṭha bik pawl thawng zakhat le thawngkul an that. Bawipa an dungtun ruangah Bawipa, an pupa ih Pathian in hi bangtuk ih cang dingah thu a pek.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule Israel ralkap pakhat Zikhri an timi pa in siangpahrang Ahaz ih fapa Maaseiah le siangpahrang inn uktu Azrikam le thuneihnak lamah siangpahrang sangtu Elkanah pawl a that ṭheh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Judah mi cu an unau an si naón Israel ralkap in Judah nunau le nauhak thawng zahnih kai in Samaria ah an hruai ih thawngah an thlak hai. Hransaw thilri tampi tla an long ih Samaria ah an tlunpi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Culai ah Bawipa ih profet pakhat, Oded an timi Samaria khua ah a um. Raldonak ihsin a ratlungmi Israel ralkap pawl cu khawsung an luh zikah a va hmuak ih an hnenah, “Bawipa, nan pupa ih Pathian cu Judah mi parih a thin a heng ruangah Judah mi pawl cu a lo nehter a si; asinain nan thin a heng tuk ruangah suup-aw loin mi tamtuk lawmmam nan thahnak thu cu van a thleng a si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cule atu-ah Jerusalem le Judah ihsin mipa nunau ti loin nan sal ah tuah ṭheh nan tum fawn. Bawipa nan Pathian hmaiah sualnak nan tuah ve hi nan thei lo maw?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> I ngai hnik uh! Hi nan kaihmi pawl hi nan unau le nan far le pawl an si. Thlah sal ṭheh uh; culole Bawipa a thinheng in a lo hrem hai ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Saklam Ram ih hminthangzet minung pali Jehohanan ih fapa Azariah, Meshillemoth ih fapa Berekhiah, Shallum ih fapa Jehizkiah le Hadlai ih fapa Amasa in ralkap pawl ih thiltuahmi cu an lung a kim loih,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ralkap pawl hnenah, “Nan kaihmi pawl cu hinah rak hruai hlah uh. Bawipa ih hnenah kan sual zo ih kanmah hrem duh tiangin a thin kan hengter zo. Cuih tlunah kan sualnak tam sinsin dingin hi bangtuk thiltuah hi nan duh hrih,” an rak ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Curuangah ralkap pawl in an kaihmi pawl le an lonmi hransaw thilri pawl cu misenpi le an hotu pawl hnenah an pek ih,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> an lonmi hransaw thilri le hnipuan pawl zemtu dingah an kaihmi pawl sung ihsin upa pali an hril. Cuih pali pawl in an hruk dingah hnipuan nei lo pawl hnipuan le kedam an pek; ti le rawl ṭhatein an pek ih an hma pawl cu olif hriak an hnihsak. A feh thei nawn lomi pawl cu laak parah an toter ih an kaih mi zatein Judah ram, tuumkung khua an timi Jerikho khua tiang an hei kuat. Cule Israel mi pawl cu Samaria ah an tlung.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cun Edom mi pawl in Judah ram cu atu le tu an siim ih mi tampi kai in salah an hruai ṭheu. Curuangah siangpahrang Ahaz in Assiria siangpahrang Tiglath Pileser hnenah bomnak a dil.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Culaifang ah Filistin mi pawl in nitlaknak lam tlanghram le Judah ram thlanglam pawl an siim. Beth Shemesh, Aijalon le Gederoth khua pawl an lak ih tlun ah Soko, Timnah le Gimzo khua pawl le an kiangkapih ummi khawte tla an la ih an luah tata.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Judah siangpahrang Ahaz in a milai pawl parah thil mawi lo le thil dik lo tampi tuah in Bawipa a dodal ruangah Judah ramah Bawipa in harsatnak a thlenter a si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Curuangah Assiria siangpahrang Tiglath Pileser in Ahaz cu a bom lam tum loin a dodal ih harsatnak tampi a pek.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cutikah Ahaz in Biakinn paisa le thilri pawl, siangpahrang inn thilri le paisa pawl le Judah ram hotu upa pawl ih neihmi hmuahhmuah tiangin a lak ṭheh ih Assiria siangpahrang a pek; asinain a bawm duh cuang lo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ahaz sualnak cu a nasa ngaingai a si! A ram sungih harsatnak a thlen deuhdeuh tikah Bawipa ih hmaiah a sual deuhdeuh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Amah a nehtu Siria mi pawl ih khawzing hnen tiangah thawinak a pek. “Siria siangpahrang cu an khawzing in an bawm ruangah kei khal in thawinak ka pek a si ahcun in bawm ve ding,” tiah a ruat. Cumi cun amah le a ram minung parah siatsuahnak a thlenter sinsin.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cuih tlunah Biakinn beelkheng hmuahhmuah a lak ih a deen kuai ṭheh. Bawipa ih Biakinn cu a khar ih Jerusalem khawsung hmun tampi ah biakṭheng a tuah ciamco.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Judah ram khawpi ah siseh khawte ah siseh, ramdang khawzing pawl hnenih rimhmui urnak ah khuavang biaknak khawhrum hmun a tuah vivo. Cuticun a pupa ih Pathian Bawipa ih thinhengnak cu amah ih parah a thlengter sinsin.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Siangpahrang a ṭuan sungih thil a cangmi le a tuahmi dang pawl cu a thokin a cemnak tiang Judah le Israel Siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu  sungah an ngan a si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Siangpahrang Ahaz cu a thi ih Jerusalem khua ah an phum; asinain siangpahrang thlaan ahcun an phum lo. A fapa Hezekiah in a pa ih ai-ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hezekiah cu kum kul hluannga a ti in siangpahrang a ṭuan ih Jerusalem ihsin kum kul hluankua sung a uk. A nu cu Zekhariah ih fanu Abijah a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A cithlahtu Siangpahrang David bangtuk in Bawipa ih lungawinak a tuah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hezekiah siangpahrang a can kum thla khatnak ah Biakinn kotka pawl cu Hezekiah in a ong sal ih a rem sal ṭheh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cule Biakinn ih nisuahnak lam kap tual ah puithiam pawl le Levi mi pawl a kokhawm ih,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Nannih Levi mi pawl, nan pupa ih Pathian Bawipa ih Biakinn cu nan thianternak dingah nanmah nan thianter-aw hmaisa pei. Cuih hnuah Biakinn a borhhlawhtertu thil hmuahhmuah nan hlon thluh pei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kan pu le kan pa pawl cu Bawipa kan Pathian hmaiah thilsual an tuah ih a riah an siatter. Bawipa cu an hnong ih a umnak hmun an dungtun a si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Biakinn sangka pawl an khar ih an vanmi mei-inn an mitter. Israel Pathian ih Biakinn sungah rimhmui an ur nawn lo; thawinak pawl khal an pe nawn lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Curuangah Bawipa cu Judah le Jerusalem parah a thin a heng ngaingai ih an parih a tuahmi thil pawl in mi hmuahhmuah tuk a suumter. Cuih thu cu nan thei thluh ko.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kan pale pawl cu raldonak ah an thi ih kan nupi le kan faate pawl sal ah an hruai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Hiti a si ruangah Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian cu kan parih a thin a heng nawn lonak dingah amah thawn thukam tuah dingin ka ruatcat zo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Curuangah ka faale pawl, daithlang men hlah uh. A hnenih rimhmui urtu dingah le misenpi in Pathian an biak tikah hotu si dingah Bawipa in nanmah hi a lo hril zomi nan si,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A tanglam ih Levi mi pawl hin hnaṭuan cu an thok: Kohath hrin in Amasai fapa Mahath le Azariah fapa Joel, Merari hrin in Abdi fapa Kish le Jehallelel fapa Azariah, Gershon hrin in Zimnah fapa Joah le Joah fapa Eden, Elizafan hrin in Shimri le Jeuel, Asaf hrin in Zekhariah le Mattaniah, Heman hrin in Jehuel le Shimei, Jeduthun hrin in Shemaiah le Uzziel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Himi pawl in an unau Levi mi pawl cu an kokhawm ih an zatein an thianfai awknak an tuah. Cule siangpahrang ih thupek vekin Biakinn cu Bawipa ih Daan pekmi bangtuk in an thianfaiter.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Puithiam pawl cu Biakinn sungah an lut ih an thianter; a thiang lomi hmuahhmuah Biakinn tualah an suah thluh ih cutawk ihsin Levi mi pawl in Kidron Phairawn ah an fehpi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hnaṭuan cu thla khatnak thla, ni khat ni in an thok ih ni riat ni ah an ṭheh; Biakinn sungih vung luhnak khaan tla an thianfai ṭheh. Cule a dang ni riat sung, ni hleiruk ni tiang an ṭuan sal ih Biakinn cu Pathian biaknak hrangih ṭha dingin an tuah kim ṭheh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cun siangpahrang Hezekiah hnenah Levi mi pawl in thu an than ih, “Biakinn cu thawinak pawl urnak biakṭheng le beelkheng pawl, sang thianghlim hunnak cabuai le a beelkheng pawl thawn kan thiangfaiter thluh zo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Siangpahrang Ahaz in Bawipa ih hmaiah thilsual a tuah laiih a lakmi thilri pawl tla kan lak sal ih kan thianter thluh zo. Bawipa ih biakṭheng hmaiah a zatein kan ret zo,” tiah an ti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cutikah zamrangte in siangpahrang Hezekiah cun khawsung upa pawl a kokhawm ih hmun khattein Bawipa ih Biakinn ahcun an feh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Siangpahrang innsang le Judah misenpi pawl sual ngaithiamnak le Bawipa ih Biakinn thianhlimternak thawinak hrangah cawcang pasarih, tuucang pasarih, tuufaate pasarih le me pasarih an keng. Cule siangpahrang bawipa in Aaron tesinfa puithiam pawl cu biakṭheng parah cuih rannung pawl thawinakih pek dingah a fial.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Puithiam pawl cun hmaisabik ah cawcang an that; cule tuucang, cuih hnuah tuufaate an that ih cuih thisen cu biakṭheng ah a sangsang in an theh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Neta bikah me pawl cu an lak ih siangpahrang bawipa le Pathian biatu pawl misenpi in cuih me pawl parah an kut an suang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cule puithiam pawl in an that ih, siangpahrang bawipa in Israel mi hmuahhmuah hrangah mei-ur thawinak le sual ngaithiam thawinak cu tuah ding a si, tiih thu a pek bangtuk in cuih thisen cu misenpi sual ngaihthiam thawinak hrangah biakṭheng parah an thlet.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bawipa in Siangpahrang David hrangih profet a rak ṭuantu profet Gad le profet Nathan hmangin David hnenih a rak pekmi daan pawl cu siangpahrang Hezekiah in a thlun ih Levi mi pawl tla Biakinn sungah darsumsel, ṭingṭang le tingrisit pawl thawn a ret.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Levi mi pawl cu siangpahrang David ih a rak hmanmi awn-mawi thilri pawl kengin an ding ih puithiam pawl cu tawtawrawt thawn an ding.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cule Hezekiah in mei-ur thawinak pe dingah thu a pek; cutiin thawinak an pek vete in senpi pawl in Pathian thangṭhatnak hla an sak ih awnmawi tumtu pawl in an tawtawrawt le a dang tummi pawl an tum ciamco.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Biakinn ih a rami hmuahhmuah in hmun khatah Pathian an bia ih an hlasak le an tummi cu thawinak pawl an ur thluh hlan lo cat loin an tum ringring.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cule siangpahrang bawipa le senpi pawl cu an khuk an bil ih Pathian an bia.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Siangpahrang Hezekiah le Judah mi hotu pawl in David le profet Asaf ih nganmi thangṭhatnak hla pawl sak dingah Levi mi pawl an fial. An fial vekin lungawi aipuang zetin an sak ih khuk bil tahratin Pathian an bia.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cun Hezekiah in senpi pawl cu, “Atu cu nan thianghlim zo ih Bawipa hnenih lungawi langternak ah thawinak cu Amah ih hnenah pe uh,” tiah a ti. A ti vek cun an tuah ih mi hrekkhat in mei-ur thawinak hrangah lungthote in rannung pawl an pek.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> An rak kenmi pawl cu cawcang sawmsarih, tuucang zakhat le tuufaate zahnih an si ih Bawipa ih hnenah mei-ur thawinakah an pek.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Cuih tlunah misenpi ih ei dingah cawcang zaruk le tuu thawngthum thawinakah an pek.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Rannung hizat thattu dingah puithiam tlamtling in an um lo ruangah cuih hnaṭuan a cem hlan lo Levi mi pawl in an bawm. Cuih tikcu ahcun puithiam tam deuh an thiangfai awter zo. Thianhlimnak thu ahcun puithiam pawl hnakin Levi mi pawl an thu a fek deuh.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Mei-ur thawinak an pek hlei ah senpi pawl ih ei mi thawinak rannung thau pawl meisa ih ur ding le mei-ur thawinak thawn pek cih mi sabitti pawl thlet ding tla cu puithiam pawl ih ṭuanvo a si. Cuticun Biakinn ih Pathian biaknak cu a thar in an thok sal.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Pathian bomnak thawngin cuih hnaṭuan pawl cu zamrangzet ih an ṭheh thei ruangah siangpahrang Hezekiah le senpi pawl cu an lung a awi ngaingai."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Thla khatnak thla ahcun a thianghlimmi puithiam tlamtling in an um hrih lo ih misenpi tla tlamtling in Jerusalem an thlen thei hrih lo ruangah a tikcu caanah Lantak Puai cu an tuah thei lo. Cuhrangah siangpahrang Hezekiah le a kuthnuai ih bawi pawl le Jerusalem mi pawl in thla hnihnak thla ih tuah dingah an lung a kim. Cuih Puai ah ra thei dingin Israel mi le Judah mi hmuahhmuah cu siangpahrang bawipa in a sawm. Efraim le Manasseh phun pawl hnenah ca a ngan ih Israel ih Pathian Bawipa ih hminthannak hrangah Jerusalem Biakinn ih Lantak Puai ra zawh dingah a hleice in sawmnak ca a kuat.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Saklam ah Dan ihsin thlanglam ah Beersheba tiang, Israel mi hmuahhmuah sawm ih kum dang hnakin Jerusalem ah mi tam deuh ngaingai ra ih Daan vekin Lantak Puai tuah dingih an tawlrel ruangah siangpahrang bawipa le misenpi pawl cu an ai a puang ngaingai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Siangpahrang le a kuthnuai bawi pawl ih thupek vekin Judah ram le Israel ram sungah mi an thlah ih an mi sawmnak cu hiti in an ngan: “Israel mi ulenau, Assiria mi in kan ram an neh naón nannih cu nan luat. Atu cu Abraham ih Pathian, Isaak ih Pathian le Jakob ih Pathian Bawipa ih hnenah kir thlang uhla, amah tla nan hnenah a kir ve ding.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bawipa an Pathian hmaiah rinsantlak loih a rak ummi nan pupa le nan unau Israel mi vek cun um nawn hlah uh. Nan theih thluh vekin annih pawl cu Bawipa in nasazet in a hrem a si.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Anmah vekin nan lung ruh hlah seh; Bawipa ih thu cu thlun sawn uh. Nan parah Bawipa cu a thin a heng nawn lonak dingah Bawipa nan Pathian in a kumkhua ih thianghlim dingah a tuahmi Jerusalem Biakinn ah ra in Amah ra bia uh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bawipa hnenih nan kirsal a si ahcun nan unau sungkhat pawl hruaihlo tahrat in thawngih a thlatu pawl khal in an parah zaangfah lainatnak thinlung an nei ding ih inn ah an tlunter ding a si. Bawipa nan Pathian cu zaangfahnak le lainatnak neitu a si ih Amaió hnen ih nan kir asile a lo pom hai ding,” tiah an ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cule an mi thlahmi pawl cu Efraim le Manasseh ram sungih khua kipah an feh ih saklam bik Zebulun ram tiang an hung thleng; asinain misenpi in an rak hnihsan ih caponak men ah an rak hman hai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Asher phun, Manasseh phun le Zebulun phun sungin mi hrekkhat cu Jerusalem khua ah ra duhtu an um.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule Judah mi lakah Pathian hna a ṭuan ih siangpahrang bawipa le a kuthnuai bawi pawl thupekmi vekin Bawipa ih thu thlun dingah senpi pawl cu tumtahnak bangrep an nei.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Thla hnihnak thla ah, Thilnu tello Sang Puai tuah dingah minung tam ngaingai Jerusalem khua ah an ra.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Jerusalem khawsung ih thawinak le rimhmui urnak biakṭheng a ummi pawl an bal ṭheh ih Kidron Horkuam ah an hlon.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule cuih thla ni hleili ni ah Lantak Puai hrang thawinak ih tuu pawl an that. A thianghlim lomi puithiam le Levi mi pawl cu an ning a zah tuk ruangah Bawipa ih hnenah thianhlimnak an tuah copcop ih cuticun Biakinn sungah thawinak an pe ve.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Pathian ih siahhlawh Moses Daan pekmi bangtuk in Biakinn sungah cun umnak an co ve. Levi mi pawl in thawinak hrangih rannung thisen cu puithiam hnenah an pek ih puithiam pawl in biakṭheng parah an theh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Mi tampi cu mithiang lo an si ruangah Lantak Puai hrangih tuu pawl an that thei lo; curuangah an ai-ah Levi mi pawl in an that ih Bawipa ih hnenah tuu cu an pek.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cuih tlunah Efraim phun, Manasseh phun, Issakhar phun le Zebulun phun sung ihsin a rami mi tampi cu thianternak a tuah hrih lo mi an si ih Lantak Puai cu a daan loin an tuah. Cutikah Siangpahrang Hezekiah in an ai-ah thla a cam ih,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Maw Bawipa, kan pupa ih Pathian, mithiang lo an si naón thinlungtak teih a lo betu pawl cu na zaangfahnak thawn ngaithiam hramhram aw,” a ti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bawipa in Hezekiah thlacamnak cu a theihsak ih cu pawl cu a ngaithiam; harsatnak zianghman an parah a thlenter lo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Jerusalem khua ih a rami hmuahhmuah in Thilnu tello Sang Puai cu lungawi aipuangte in ni sarih sung an tuah; ni khat hnu ni khat puithiam le Levi mi pawl in Bawipa cu an thaneih zat  in an thangṭhat.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bawipa biaknak ah mi hruai daan a thiamzettu Levi mi pawl cu siangpahrang Hezekiah in a lawm hai. Cuticun ni sarih sung puai an tuah ih Bawipa ih hnenah remnak thawinak an pek ih an pupa ih Pathian cu an thangṭhat.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cuih hnuah an zatein ni sarih sung puai tuah pehsal dingah an lung a kimih a dang ni sarih sung lungawi aipuang in puai cu an tuah sal.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Siangpahrang Hezekiah in cuih puai ih misenpi pawl ei dingah cawcang thawngkhat le tuu thawng sarih a pek ih a kuthnuai bawi pawl in cawcang thawngkhat le tuu thawnghra an pe ve. Puithiam tampi in anmah thianhlimnak an tuah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cuticun mi hmuahhmuah Judah mi, puithiam pawl, Levi mi pawl, saklam ram ihsin a rungmi pawl le Israel le Judah ram sungih a um ringring mi ramdangmi pawl tla an zatein an lung a awi ngaingai.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Jerusalem khawpi cu lungawinak in a khat; cubangtuk lungawinak cu David fapa Siangpahrang Solomon san hnuah a um dah lo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Puithiam le Levi mi pawl in senpi pawl cu Bawipa ih thlawsuah an dil sak. Vancung a inn ihsin an thlacamnak cu Pathian in a thei ih a co sak hai a si."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> An puai tuah mi an ṭheh tikah Israel mi hmuahhmuah an zatein Judah ramsung khua kipah an feh ih lungphun thianghlim pawl an khuai, khawzingnu Asherah hrang timi thingphun thianghlim pawl an hau ih biakṭheng le an khuavang biaknak hmun pawl an siatbal ṭheh. Judah ram lawngah si loin Efraim ram, Benjamin ram le Manasseh ram tla ah cubangtuk in an tuah ih cuih hnuah an inn ciarah an tlung.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Siangpahrang Hezekiah in puithiam le Levi mi pawl ih hnaṭuan cu a thar in a rem sal ih cuticun puithiam le Levi mipawl ṭuanvo an nei fingfing. An hnaṭuan cu mei-ur thawi peknak, remnak thawinak le Biakinn sung Pathian biaknak ih tel ding le Biakinn sung khaan kipah Pathian thangṭhat le Pathian hnenih lungawinak sim tla an si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Zinglam le zanlam ih mei-ur thawinak pekmi hrangah le Sabbath ni le Thla Thar Puai hrangah siseh, Bawipa ih Daan pekmi bangtuk in tuah ding a ṭulmi puai dangdang hrangah siseh, siangpahrang Hezekiah in a cawrual le a tuurual sungin rannung tampi a pek.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cuih tlunah Bawipa ih Daan vekih puithiam le Levi pawl in an tikcu neihzat caan an pek theinak dingah misenpi pawl in covo an neih mi thawinak pawl cu rak pe dingin siangpahrang in Jerusalem khuami hnenah thu a pek.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Siangpahrang thupekmi an theih vete in Israel mi pawl in laksawng an rak kengih an neihmi lakih a ṭha bik sangphut, sabitti, olif hriak, khuaitizu le an lo ihsin a suak mi dangdang an pek; cule an neihmi hmuahhmuah sungin ṭhen hra ṭhen khat tla an pek.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Judah khua pawl ih a ummi hmuahhmuah in, Israel mi siseh, Judah mi siseh, an caw le an tuu pawl ṭhen hra ṭhen khat an pek; cuih tlunah Bawipa hnenih an hlan ciami thilri thiang sung in ṭhenhra ṭhenkhat an pek fawn. An pekmi cu vuun liailiai in a um.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Thla thumnak thla in an laksawng pek cu an thok ih thla sarih thla tiang cat loin an pek.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Siangpahrang Hezekiah le a kuthnuai bawi pawl in cubangtuk in vuun liailiai ih an pekmi laksawng an hmuh tikah Bawipa an thangṭhat ih Israel mi pawl hrangah thlawsuah an dil sak.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cuih laksawng thu cu siangpahrang bawipa in puithiam le Levi mi pawl hnenih a suh tikah,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Zadok tesinfa Puithiam Sang Azariah in, “Bawipa  Biakinn ih laksawng an rak ken thok ihsin ei-in ding cu tlamtling zetin kan nei ih a hleimi khal hitluk tam hi a si. Bawipa in a minung pawl mal a sawm ruangah hitluk tam hi kan nei a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutikah Bawipa ih Biakinn kapih thil retnak khaan pawl sak dingin siangpahrang in thu a pek;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> a thupek vekin an tuah ih misenpi ih pekmi thawhlawm, laksawng le ṭhen hra ṭhen khat pawl cu cutawkah felzet in an ret. Levi mi Konaniah cu a kiltu ah an ret ih a unau Shimei cu a sangtu ah an ret.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> An kuthnuai ih hnaṭuantu dingah Levi mi pahra an ret ih Jehiel, Azaziah, Nahath, Asahel, Jerimoth, Jozabad, Eliel, Ismakhiah, Mahath le Benaiah an si. Hi an retmi pawl cu siangpahrang Hezekiah le Puithiam Sang Azariah thupek vekih retmi an si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Biakinn Nisuahnak lam Kotka kiltu Levi mi Imnah ih fapa Kore cu Bawipa hnenih an rak kenmi laksawng a rak sangtu le a zemtu a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Puithiam umnak khua dangah cuih hnaṭuan cu Levi mi amah bawmtu dangdang in an ṭuan; a bawmtu pawl cu Eden, Miniamin, Jeshua, Shemaiah, Amariah le Shekaniah an si. An hnaṭuan mi zoh in an unau Levi mi pawl hnenah a tam a mal bangrep in an zem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cu hrin kha hrin, tiin an zem lo. Biakinn ih hnaṭuan nei mipa kum sawmthum le a tlunlam hmuahhmuah cu an hnaṭuan thlun in an zem ciar a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Puithiam pawl cu an hrin ciar in hnaṭuan an nei; Levi mi mipa kum kul le a tlunlam pawl cu a bur a bur in hnaṭuan an nei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> An hnaṭuan sunglawi cu ziangtik caan khalah a ṭuantu ding an si hrangah an nupi, an fanote, an fanu le an fapa pawl thawn siarcih thluh an si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Aaron tesinfa khawsungih a ummi puithiam pawl, a si lole khua kiangkapih rannung tlannak ram sungih a ummi puithiam pawl lakah ṭuanvo neitu mipa an um ih anmah pawl in puithiam sungkhat mipa hmuahhmuah le Levi miphun mipum siarnak sungih a telmi hmuahhmuah cu an covo ciar an zem hai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Judah ram sung hmuahhmuah ah Siangpahrang Hezekiah in Bawipa a Pathian ih lungawinak le a dikmi thil a tuah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Biakinn hrang hnaṭuannak ah siseh, Daan thu thlunnak ah siseh, thinlung taktein Pathian hnenah a pek awk ruangah a hlawhtling a si."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hezekiah in Bawipa rinsan in hna a ṭuan ih hi bangtuk thil pawl a tuah hnuah, Assiria siangpahrang Sennakherib in Judah ram a do; ralhruang ih kulhmi khua tampi a kulh ih a ralkap pawl cu khua kulhnak lungdawl pawl siatsuah thluh dingin thu a pek.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Sennakherib in Jerusalem khawpi tla do a tum a si, ti kha Hezekiah in a hmuh tikah,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Assiria ralkap pawl Jerusalem an thlen khalle tidai in ding nei hlah hai seh, tiah siangpahrang Hezekiah le a kuthnuai ih bawi pawl in khawpi lengih a ummi an dawhhna pawl kha a phih thluh an tum. Bawi pawl ho in khawsungmi tampi an pok ih dawhhna ti hmuahhmuah an phit thluh; curuangah tidai zianghman a luang nawn lo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule siangpahrang in raldo ih an ṭannak ding pawl cu ṭha sinsin in a tuah; khawpi kulhnak phar a rem; a tlunah ralvennak innsanghlei a sak; khawpi kulhnak lenglam phar tla a dawl. Jerusalem khua hlun nisuahnak lamih a ummi raldo ṭannak hrangih an sakmi pawl khal a rem. Feipi le ralphaw tam ngaingai a tuah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Jerusalem khawsungmi mipa hmuahhmuah cu ralbawi pawl a hoter; khawpi kotka kiang mualrawn ah an zatein a pumkhawmter ih an hnenah forhnak thu a sim:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Cakzet le ralṭhazet in um uh; nan thin khal nau hlah seh. Assiria siangpahrang siseh, a homi ralkap pawl siseh, ṭih hlah uh. An lamih ṭangtu hnakin kan lamih ṭangtu a cak sawn.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Anih a neihmi cu milai cahnak lawng a si; asinain kannih cun in bawmtu le kan hrangih dotu dingah Bawipa kan Pathian kan nei a si,” tiah a ti. Cuih thu an theih tikah senpi pawl cu an tha a tho ngaingai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cuih hnuah Sennakherib le a ralkap pawl cu Lakhish ih an um laiah Jerusalem khua ih a ummi siangpahrang Hezekiah le Judah mi pawl hnenah Sennakherib in mi a run thlah ih hiti in thu a run cah:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Assiria siangpahrang keimah Sennakherib ih thucah mi hi rak ruat uh: Judah mi pawl, ziang nan rinsan ruangah so ral ih kulhmi Jerusalem khawsungah nan um?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ‘Assiria siangpahrang kut sung thleng lo dingin Bawipa kan Pathian in in hum ding,’ tiah Hezekiah in a lo sim; sikhalsehla a lo bum a si; rawl lo le ti loin nan thi ding.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bawipa Pathian biaknak hmun pawl le biakṭheng pawl a siatbal thluhtu cu amah Hezekiah a si ih Judah le Jerusalem cu biakṭheng pakhat lawngah Pathian biak dingah le rimhmui ur dingah a lo fialtu cu amah thotho a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Miphun dang le ramdang pawl tlunah ka pupa pawl in siseh, keimah in siseh, kan thiltuah mi pawl nan thei thluh zo lo maw? Zo ih pathian tal in an minung pawl Assiria siangpahrang keimah ih kut sung thleng lo dingah an hum thei dah maw?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ziangtik talah hi kan siatsuahmi miphun pawl ih pathian pawl in an ram cu kan kut ihsin an runsuak dah maw? ‘Kan Pathian in in hum ding,’ tiah ziangtinso nannih bul nan zum thei?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hezekiah bummi le hruaisualmi si duh hlah uh, a zum khal zum hlah uh. Ziangbangtuk miphun ih pathian hman in an miphun cu Assiria siangpahrang kut cun an hum thei dah lo. Nanmah pawl ih pathian sinsin cun a lo hum thei lo ding!” a ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sennakherib ih thlahmi palai pawl in Bawipa Pathian le a siahhlawh Hezekiah an hmuhsuamnak cu hi hnakih luar deuh in an ṭongmi a um lai hrih.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cuih tlunah Assiria siangpahrang in Israel ih Pathian dodal nautatnak ah ca hiti in a ngan: “Miphun dangdangih khawzing pawl in an minung pawl cu ka cahnak kut sungin an run thei dah lo; Hezekiah ih Pathian khal in a minung pawl cu ka kut sungin a run thei cuang lo ding,” a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Jerusalem khawpi kulhnak phar parih a ummi Jerusalem mi pawl hro duh ah le ṭhihṭhaih duh ah cuih palai pawl cun Hebru ṭong in cuih thu cu ringzet in an aupi ciamco.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Milai kutih tuahcopmi miphundang ih khawzing pawl ih thuhla an rel vekin Jerusalem ih Pathian thuhla khal an rel ve a si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cutikah Siangpahrang Hezekiah le Amoz fapa profet Isaiah in thla an cam ih bomnak dil in Pathian hnenah an au.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bawipa in vancungmi pakhat a thlah ih cuih vancungmi cun ralṭhazet Assiria ralkap pawl le an ralbawi pawl cu an riahhmun ah a that ṭheh hai. Curuangah Assiria siangpahrang cu ningzak le mithmai sia in a ramah a kirta. Cule a khawzing biaknak innih a luh tikah a fapa hrekkhat pawl in an ralnam in an sun ih a thi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cuticun Bawipa in siangpahrang Hezekiah le Jerusalem khuami pawl cu Assiria siangpahrang Sennakherib le a ral pawl kut in a hum a si. Bawipa in an ram khuazakip ah daihnak a umter.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Jerusalem khua ah mi tampi an ra ih Bawipa hnenih thawinak le Hezekiah hrangah laksawng tampi an keng; cuih ihsin thok in miphun dang hmuahhmuah in Hezekiah cu an upatzet.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cuih caanah Hezekiah cu thizik in a na. Bawipa ih hnenah thla a cam ih Bawipa in a thlacamnak a saang ih a dam ding tiah hminsinnak a pek.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sikhalsehla Hezekiah cu a hngal tuk ih Bawipa in a parih thil ṭha a tuahmi hrangah lungawinak zianghman a langter lo; curuangah Judah le Jerusalem mi parah Bawipa a thin a heng.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Asinain Hezekiah le Jerusalem mi pawl cu an lung a nemsal ruangah Hezekiah nunsung ahcun Bawipa ih hremnak zianghman an tong lo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hezekiah cu a lian ngaingai ih mi hmuahhmuah in upatnak an pek. A sui le a ngun, lungmankhung le rimhmui, ralphaw le a dang thilri mankhung pawl retnak ah inn tampi a sak.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cuih tlunah a neihmi rawl le sabitti le olif hriak retnak ah inn pawl a sak; a caw retnak ah caw inn a sak ih a tuu retnak ah tuu inn a sak.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cuih hlei ah Pathian in tuu le caw tampi a pek ih sumsaw dangdang tla tampi a pek ruangah khua tampi a din.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Gihon Cerhti luannak a kham ih leihnuai in Jerusalem khawpi kulhnak pharih sunglam tiang tidai luang ko ih a tuahtu khal amah siangpahrang Hezekiah a si. A thiltuah mi hmuahhmuah ah Hezekiah cu hlawhtlinnak a nei.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> A thinlung le a ziaza theih duh ah Pathian in Hezekiah cu a duhduh in a tlanleenter; culai hmanah a ram sungih mangbangza thil a cangmi pawl zingzoi dingah Babilon siangpahrang in a palai pawl a run thlah.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Siangpahrang Hezekiah in a tuahmi dangdang le Bawipa hnenih rinsannak thawn a ṭuanmi dang pawl cu Amoz Fapa Profet Isaiah Langnak Hmuhmi Cabu  le Judah le Israel Siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu  sungah an ngan a si.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hezekiah cu a thi ih siangpahrang thlaan tlunta lamah an phum. A thih tikah Judah mi le Jerusalem khua mi hmuahhmuah in upatnak an pek. A fapa Manasseh in a ai-ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Manasseh cu kum hleihnih a ti ah Judah siangpahrang a ṭuan ih Jerusalem ihsin kum sawmnga le kum nga sung a uk.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bawipa ih hmaiah thilṭha lo a tuah ih a sual a si. Israel mi pawl Kanaan ram an rak luh laiih a rak um cia, Bawipa in a dawimi pawl ih thil tuahmi thlun in fihnungza thil pawl a tuah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Manasseh in a pa Hezekiah ih a rak balmi khuavang an rak biaknak hmun pawl cu a sak sal. Culawng si loin Baal khawzing biaknak ah biakṭheng pawl a don; Asherah khawzingnu lem a tuah ih tlunah arsi pawl tla a bia.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bawipa ih Biakinn sung ‘Kumkhua in Keimah in biaknak hmunah,’ tiah Bawipa Amah in a rak timi ahcun khuavang biakṭheng pawl a don.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Biakinn tual pahnih ah arsi biaknak biakṭheng pawl a don.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hinnom Phairawn ah a fapa pawl mei-ur thawinak ah a pek. Ai a zing, dawi a hmang, kutṭial a zohter, tin a zoh. Bawipa ih hmaiah thilṭha lozet a tuah ih Bawipa ih thin a hengter.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bawipa Biakinn sungah milem a ret. Bawipa in David le a fapa Solomon hnenah, “Hi Jerusalem khua, hi Biakinn hmun cu keimah in biaknak dingah Israel miphun hleihnih ih ramsung ihsin ka hrilmi hmun a si.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Israel mi pawl in ka thukham le ka thupekmi hmuahhmuah an thlun ih ka siahhlawh Moses in an hnenih a pekmi Daan pawl kimtein an tuah a si ahcun an pupa hnenih ka pekmi hih ram ihsin zohman in an dawi hai lo ding,” tiin a rak sim hnawhsan ciami Biakinn sung rori ah milem cu a ret a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bawipa ih minung Israel mi pawl Kanaan ram an luh laiih Bawipa in a dawihlomi miphun pawl ih sualnak hnak hmanin a luar sawnmi sualnak sungah Judah mi pawl cu Manasseh in a hruailut hai a si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bawipa in Manasseh le a minung pawl cu ralrinnak a pek naón an ngai duh lo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Curuangah Bawipa in Assiria ralbawi pawl cu Judah ram a doter. Cutikah Manasseh cu an kai ih a hnar ah sio an thlaih; thir cikcin thawn hreng an sut ih Babilon ah an hruai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cutiin vansaanglam ih a um ruangah a lung nem in Bawipa a Pathian hnenah a hoikir sal ih thlacam in Bawipa ih bomnak a dil.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Manasseh thlacamnak cu Pathian in a theihsak ih Jerusalem ah kirter sal in Judah ram cu a ukter sal. Cuticun Manasseh in Bawipa cu Pathian ngaingai a si, ti a thei ngah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cuih hnuah Manasseh in Jerusalem khua kulhnak phardawl cu nisuahnak lamih ummi Gihon Cerh rawn ihsin saklam Nga Kotka le Ofel an timi khua tiang a dawl ih saang sinsin in a tuah. Judah ram sung ralhruang ih kulhmi khua kipah ralbawi pakhat le a kuthnuai ralkap pawl a ret vivo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule Biakinn ih a rak retmi ramdang khawzing pawl le milem pawl cu a lak ṭheh ih tlunah Biakinn an saknak tlangtluan le Jerusalem khawsung ih a ummi khuavang biakṭheng pawl hmuahhmuah a bal ṭheh. Cuih pawl cu a lak ih Jerusalem khua lengah a hlonhlo ṭheh a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bawipa biaknak ih biakṭheng cu a rem ih remnak thawinak le lungawi thawinak pawl a pek. Judah mi hmuahhmuah cu Bawipa Israel ih Pathian bia dingah a forh ciamco.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Senpi pawl cun hmun dangdang khalah thawinak an tuah; asinain an pekmi ngaingai cu Bawipa ih hnen lawngah a si.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Manasseh ih tuahmi dangdang, a Pathian hnenih a thlacam mi le Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian hminin profet pawl in a hnenih thu an phuanmi pawl cu kimtein Israel Siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu  sungah an ngan a si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Siangpahrang Manasseh thlacamnak le Pathian ih a lehnak, sualnak le ṭhat lonak a tuah mi pawl, khuavang biaknak le Asherah khawzingnu lem a tuahmi pawl le milem a biaknak thu pawl cu kimtein Profet Pawl Thuanthu Cabu  sungah an ngan a si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Manasseh cu a thi ih siangpahrang inn ah an phum; cule a fapa Amon in a ai-ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Amon cu Judah siangpahrang a ṭuan ah kum kul hluanhnih a ti ih Jerusalem in kum hnih sung a uk.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> A pa Manasseh vekin Bawipa ih hmaiah a sual ih a pa ih rak biakmi milem pawl a bia ve.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Asinain a pa vek a si lo; a thinlung a nem loih Bawipa khal a hoikir sal lo; a pa hnakin a sual a luar a si.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cun a kuthnuai ih bawi pawl in an phiar ih a siangpahrang inn sungah Amon cu an that.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Asinain Amon thattu pawl cu Judah mi pawl in an that ve lala ih Amon fapa Josiah cu siangpahrang ah an tuah."
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Josiah cu Judah siangpahrang a ṭuan ah kum riat a ti ih Jerusalem ihsin kum sawmthum le kum khat sung a uk.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bawipa ih hmaiah thilṭha a tuah ih Bawipa ih lung a awiter. A pupa siangpahrang David dung a thlun ih Pathian ih thupekmi hmuahhmuah feltein a thlun.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Josiah cu siangpahrang a ṭuannak kum riatnak, mino a si lai ihsin a pupa siangpahrang David ih Pathian biak hram a thok. Kum li hnuah khuavang an biaknak hmun pawl, Asherah khawzingnu ih lem pawl le milem dangdang pawl cu a bal ciamco.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A thupek vekin a minung pawl in Baal an biaknak hrangih biakṭheng pawl cu an siatbal thluh; a kiangih rimhmui urnak biakṭheng pawl an deng kuai ṭheh ih Asherah khawzing nu ih lem pawl le a dang milem pawl cu an rialdip thluh hnuah a vut cu thawinak a rak petu mi pawl ih thlaan ah an phulh ciamco.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Khuavang puithiam pawl ih ruh cu an khuavang biaknak biakṭheng parah a ur ih cuticun Judah le Jerusalem cu Josiah in a thianfaiter sal.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Manasseh ram, Efraim ram le Simeon ram sung hmunkip le khua kipah, saklam ah Naftali thlengin cubangtuk ṭhiamṭhiam in a tuah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Saklam Ramsung khuazakip ah biakṭheng pawl a siat sal, Asherah lem pawl a hau ṭheh, milem pawl a rialdip ṭheh ih rimhmui urnak biakṭheng pawl a den kuai thluh. Cuih hnuah Jerusalem ah a kir.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Siangpahrang Josiah in Judah ram a uknak kum hleiriatnak kum, a ramsung le Bawipa ih Biakinn sungih khuavang biaknak a thianfaiter hnuah, Josiah cun Bawipa Pathian ih Biakinn rem dingah mi pathum: Azaliah ih fapa Shafan, Jerusalem uktu bawi Maaseiah le bawi upa pakhat Joahaz ih fapa Joah pawl ṭuanvo a pek.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Levi mi Biakinn kiltu pawl in Efraim mi, Manasseh mi, Saklam Ram mi pawl, Judah mi Benjamin mi le Jerusalem khawsung mi pawl hnen ihsin Biakinn ih paisa an rak kenmi an khawm ih Puithiam Sang Hilkiah hnenah an fehpi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cuih paisa cu Biakinn an remnak lamih hnaṭuan hotu pawl hnenah an pek ih,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> inn saktu le zungthiam pawl hlawhman an pek ih cuih tlunah lungto leinak le Judah siangpahrang daithlan ruangih a siatmi inn pawl remnak hrangih a ṭulmi zanthing pawl leinak ah an hmang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cuih hnaṭuantu pawl cu mifelzet le rinsan tlakzet an si. An hotu pawl cu mi pali: Levi mi Merari hrin Jahath le Obadiah, Levi mi Kohath hrin Zekhariah le Meshullam an si. Levi mi cu an zatein hlathiam an si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> A dang Levi mi pawl in thilri phurtu pawl an ho ih hnaṭuantu dangdang zohtu tla an si; a dang Levi mi pawl cu sungṭuan, cazi le sangka kiltu tla an si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Thilri retnak khaan ihsin paisa an suah laiah Hilkiah in Moses hnenih Pathian pekmi Daan, Bawipa ih Daan cabu a sar ngah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cutikah Hilkiah in, “Hi Biakinn sungah Daan cabu ka sar,” tiah Shafan a sim. Hilkiah in cuih cabu cu Shafan a pek ih,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Shafan in siangpahrang hnenah a fehpi. Shafan in siangpahrang hnenah cun, “Na thupekmi bangtuk in ziang hmuahhmuah kan tuah ṭheh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Biakinn sungih retmi paisa tla kan suah ih hnaṭuantu pawl le an hotu pawl hnenah kan pek,” a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Cun hinah Hilkiah ih i pekmi cabu a um,” tiah a ti. Cule siangpahrang hnenah ringzet in a siar.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cumi cu siangpahrang in a theih tikah a ninghang in a hnipuan a thlek.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cule Puithiam Sang Hilkiah, Shafan ih fapa Ahikam, Mikaiah ih fapa Abdon, cangantu Shafan le siangpahrang kiltu Asaiah pawl a ko ih an hnenah hiti in thu a pek,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Feh uh la keimah le Israel le Judah ram sungih a taanglai mi minung pawl hrangah Bawipa va ron uh. Hi cabu ih a zirh mi hi feltein theisuak uh. Hi cabu ih tuah ding a timi kan pupa pawl in an tuah loih Bawipa ih thu an ngai lo ruangah kan parah Bawipa a thin a heng a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Siangpahrang thupek vekin Hilkiah le a rualpi pawl cu Jerusalem khawthar ih a ummi nunau profet Huldah an timi tong dingah an feh. Hasrah ih tupa, Tikvah ih fapa Shallum cu Huldah pasal a si ih Biakinn hnipuan pawl kilkhawitu a si. Cule annih in an tonmi thuhla pawl cu Huldah an sim.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cutikah Huldah in, “Siangpahrang hnenah va kir uhla,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bawipa in, ‘Siangpahrang hnenih nan siarmi cabu sungih nganmi thusia siatcamnak vekin Jerusalem le misenpi pawl cu ka hrem hai ding.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Keimah in hnong ih khawzing dang hnenah thawinak an pek; hiti ih an tuahmi ruangah an parah ka thin a heng a si. Jerusalem parih ka thinhengnak cu a dai lo ding.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Siangpahrang amah hrangah Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian Keimah in hiti in ka sim: Hi cabu sungih nganmi thu na ngai ih,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Jerusalem le a minung pawl ka hrem ding thu na theih tikah na hnipuan thlek le ṭap rero in na siir aw ih na thinlung a nem ruangah na thlacamnak ka thei zo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Jerusalem ka hremnak cu na hmu man lo ding. Daite in na caan ka cemter ding,’ a ti va ti uh,” tiah a sim. Cuih thu thawn Hilkiah le a rualpi pawl cu siangpahrang Josiah hnenah an kir.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang Josiah in Judah le Jerusalem hotu pawl a ko ṭheh ih,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> hmun khatah puithiam pawl le Levi mi pawl le Jerusalem khawsung mi pawl thawn mifarah milian ti loin Biakinn ah an zatein an feh. Biakinn sungih an hmuhmi thukam cabu cu a zatein ring zetin an hmaiah siangpahrang bawipa in a siar.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cule Josiah cu a siangpahrang ṭhuam kiangah a ding ih cuih cabu sungih a ummi vekin, thukamnak sungih kam awkmi pawl tuah suak dingah siseh, Bawipa ih thukham cu a thinlung le a thazaang zatein thlun dingah le Bawipa ih thu ngai dingah Bawipa ih hnenah thukamnak a tuah.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Cuih thukamnak thlun dingah Jerusalem ih a ummi hmuahhmuah le Benjamin mi pawl cu thutiamnak a tuahter. Cuticun Jerusalem mi pawl in an pupa ih Pathian hnenih an tiamkammi thukam hmuahhmuah cu an thlun.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Cule siangpahrang Josiah in Israel ram sungih a ummi fihnungza milem pawl cu a siatsuah ṭheh. A nun sungah senpi pawl cun an pupa ih Pathian Bawipa thlun cu an pialsan nawn lo."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang Josiah in Bawipa ih hmin thangṭhatnak ah Lantak Puai cu Jerusalem khua ah a tuah; thla hmaisa bik ni hleilinak ni ah cuih puai cu an tuah ih rannung pawl an that.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Puithiam pawl hnenah Biakinn ih an hnaṭuan dingmi a pek ih felte ih tuahsuak dingah a forh hai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bawipa hnenih thianhlimter mi, Israel mi zirhtu Levi mi pawl tla thu a cah ih, an hnenah, “David fapa siangpahrang Solomon ih sakmi Biakinn sungah Thukam Kuang cu ret uh. Hi Thukam Kuang cu hmunkhat ihsin hmun dangah nan phur nawn lo pei ih Bawipa nan Pathian le Amah ih minung Israel mi pawl ih hna lawnglawng nan ṭuan pei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Siangpahrang David le a fapa siangpahrang Solomon in ṭuanvo an lo pek bangtuk in Biakinn ah nan sungkhat fingfing in ṭuanvo nan lak pei.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Israel mi sungah innsang pakhatkhat bom an ṭul tikah bawm theitu si ding in nan zuam pei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nanmah in Lantak Puai hrangih tuu le me pawl cu nan that pei. Cule Bawipa in Moses hnenih a pekmi Daan bangtuk in nan unau Israel mi pawl ih an thlun ve nak dingah nanmah cu thiangfaiter aw uhla, thawinak pekmi pawl cu timtuah uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Siangpahrang Josiah in Lantak Puai tikcu ih misenpi pawl hrangah amah ih rannung rual pawl sung ihsin tuu le tuuno, le menote a zate ah thawng sawmthum a pek; cawcang khal thawng thum a pek.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A kuthnuai bawi pawl khal in senpi pawl, puithiam pawl le Levi mi pawl hrangah an pek ve. Biakinn kiltu upa pawl: Puithiam Sang Hilkiah, Zekhariah le Jehiel in cuih puai tikcu ih thawinak pek dingah puithiam pawl hnenah tuuno le meno thawng hnih le zaruk, le cawcang zathum an pek.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Levi mi hotu pawl Konaniah, Shemaiah le a unau Nethanel, Hashabiah, Jeiel le Jozabad pawl in tuuno, le meno thawng nga le cawcang zanga cu Levi mi pawl ih thawinak hrangah an pek.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Lantak Puai hrangih ziang hmuahhmuah an tawlrel ṭheh tikah siangpahrang ih thupekmi vekin puithiam le Levi mi pawl cu an hnaṭuannak hmun ciarah an um.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Tuu le me pawl thah an si tikah Levi mi in a phaw an hawk ih a thisen cu puithiam pawl in biakṭheng ah an theh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule Moses Daan sung vekih mei-ur thawinak an pek theinak dingah rannung sa cu sungkhat sungkhat ciarin misenpi pawl an zem.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> A daan bangtuk in Lantak Puai thawinak sa cu Levi mi pawl in meisa ah an em ih thawinak thianghlim cu beel le thir beel le uhkang tumpipi in an suang ih senpi pawl hnenah zamrangte in an zem.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cu ṭheh hnu lawngah Levi mi pawl in anmah ih hrang le Aaron tesinfa puithiam pawl hrangah sa an zem; ziangahtile mei-ur thawinak le a thau pawl pekmi an urnak ah puithiam pawl cu zan khawthim tiang an man hrimhrim lo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cun Asaf hrin hla satu pawl tla siangpahrang David ih thupekmi vekin an hnaṭuannak hmun ciarah an um. Asaf hrin pawl, Heman le siangpahrang profet Jeduthun le Biakinn kotka kiltu pawl cu an hnaṭuannak ihsin hmun dangih feh rero a ṭul lo; ziangahtile an hrangah Levi mi pawl in ziang hmuahhmuah an tawlrel sak a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Curuangah siangpahrang Josiah ih thupek vekin Lantak Puai ulhnak le biakṭheng parih mei-ur thawinak pekmi pawl le cuih ni ih Bawipa biaknak ziang hmuahhmuah cu famkim zetin an tuah thluh a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cutawkih a telmi Israel mi hmuahhmuah in Lantak Puai le Thilnu tello Sang Puai cu ni sarih sung an tuah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Profet Samuel san hnuah Lantak Puai cu hi vekin an tuah dah lo. Israel siangpahrang dang khal in Lantak Puai cu siangpahrang Josiah in puithiam pawl, Levi mi pawl, Judah mi, Israel mi le Jerusalem khawsungmi pawl thawn a tuahmi vek cun an tuah dah lo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Josiah siangpahrang a ṭuan kum hleiriat kumah hi Lantak Puai cu an tuah a si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Siangpahrang Josiah in Bawipa ih Biakinn hrangah hibangtuk hna a ṭuan ṭheh hnuah, Izipt siangpahrang Neko in Eufrates Tivapi kapih ummi Karkhemish ah raldo dingin a ralkap pawl thawn an pok. Cumi cu Josiah in kham a tum.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cutikah Neko in Josiah hnenah thu a cah ih, “Maw Judah siangpahrang, hi ka raldo ding mi hi i hnaihnok duh hlah, nang thawn zianghman a seng aw lo; nangmah do dingah ka ra lo. Ka ral pawl do ding lawngah ka ra ih Pathian in zamrangte ih feh dingah i fial a si. Pathian cu ka hnenah a ṭang ih Amah cu do duh hlah; na do asile a lo siatsuah sawn ding,” a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sikhalsehla Josiah cun a ngai lo ih a do tum thotho; curuangah theihthiam lo dingin a tuah-aw ih raldonak ah a feh. Siangpahrang Neko hmangin Pathian ih thusimmi cu a ngai duh lo ih Megiddo phairawn ah raldo dingin a feh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> An do awk tikah Izipt conkiang in siangpahrang Josiah cu a ngah. Cutikah a siahhlawh pa hnenah, “I tlanpi aw! Besiazet in in ngah a si,” a ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> A rangleng ihsin an cawi ih a rangleng pahnihnak ah an ret ih Jerusalem ah an kirpi. Cutawkah a thi ih siangpahrang thlaan ah an phum. Judah mi le Jerusalem mi pawl in a thih cu an ul ih an ṭap.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Profet Jeremiah in siangpahrang Josiah hrangah ṭahhla a phuah ih an siangpahrang an ṭah tikah hla satu pawl in nunau siseh mipa siseh, cuih ṭahhla cun an ṭah ṭheu. Cutiih mithi ṭah cu Israel mi daan ah a cang ih cuih hla cu ṭahhla cabu sungah a um a si.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Josiah in Bawipa a rinsannak, Daan a thlunzia,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> a uknak hramthokin a net tiang, a thiltuahmi hmuahhmuah le amah ih thuanthu cu Israel le Judah Siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu  sungah kimtein an ngan a si."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Judah mi pawl in Josiah fapa Joahaz siangpahrang ah an hril ih Jerusalem khua ah hriak an culh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Joahaz cu Judah siangpahrang a ṭuan tikah kum kul hluanthum a ti ih Jerusalem ihsin thla thum sung a uk.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Izipt siangpahrang Neko in a kaih ih thawngah a thlak; cule Judah mi in Neko cu ngun pawng zasarih le sawmnga, le sui pawng sawmsarih le pawng nga siah ah an pek.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Neko in Joahaz unau Eliakim cu Judah siangpahrang ah a tuah ih a hmin Jehoiakim ah a thleng. Joahaz cu Neko in Izipt ramah a hruai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Jehoiakim cu Judah siangpahrang a ṭuan ah kum kul hluannga a ti ih Jerusalem ihsin kum hleikhat sung a uk. Bawipa a Pathian hmaiah thil ṭha lo a tuah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Babilon siangpahrang Nebuchadnezzar in Judah ram cu a siim ih Jehoiakim cu kai tahrat in thir cikcin in an khit ih Babilon ah an hruai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nebuchadnezzar in Bawipa ih Biakinn thilri mankhung hrekkhat pawl a lak ih Babilon a siangpahrang inn ah a ret.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Jehoiakim ih tuahmi hmuahhmuah, ningsinza thil a tuahmi cu a sualnak pawl tiangin, Israel Le Judah Siangpahrang Thuanthu Cabu  sungah an ngan a si. A fapa Jehoiakhin in a ai-ah siangpahrang a run ṭuan.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Jehoiakhin cu Judah siangpahrang a ṭuan tikah kum hleiriat a ti ih Jerusalem ihsin thla thum le nihra sung a uk. Anih khal Bawipa ih hmaiah a sual.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Khawsik a reh ih ṭhal a hungsuah tikah siangpahrang Nebuchadnezzar in a kai ih Babilon ah a hruai. Bawipa ih Biakinn thilri mankhung pawl tla a phur ṭheh. Cule Nebuchadnezzar in Jehoiakhin ih unau Zedekiah cu Judah le Jerusalem siangpahrang ah a tuah.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Zedekiah cu Judah siangpahrang a ṭuan tikah kum kul hluankhat a ti ih Jerusalem ihsin kum hleikhat sung a uk.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bawipa ih hmaiah sualnak a tuah; Bawipa ih thu a phuangtu profet Jeremiah ih thusimmi a ngai lo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Zedekiah cu siangpahrang Nebuchadnezzar do dingah ral a tho. Cutikah Nebuchadnezzar in a kuthnuai um dingah Pathian hmin saal in thu a kamter. Zedekiah in Bawipa Israel ih Pathian hnenah sualsir-aw in Pathian hnenih hoikir sal a tum hrimhrim lo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cuih tlunah Judah mi hotu pawl, puithiam le misenpi pawl khal in an kiangkap ih um miphun pawl ih sualnak keneh cu an thlunih an uire a si. Cuticun Bawipa amah rori in a thianhlimter mi Biakinn cu an borhhlawhter ṭheh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bawipa, an pupa ih Pathian in a minung pawl le a Biakinn cu a zuah duh ruangah an hnenih ralrinnak pe dingah cat loin profet a thlah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Asinain Pathian ih thlahmi palai le profet pawl cu an rak hmuhsuam; an hnihsan men ih zianghman ah an siar lo. A netnak ahcun an parah Bawipa ih thinhengnak cu a luar tukih an luat theinak lamzin a um nawn lo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bawipa in Babilon siangpahrang a thlah ih Judah mi mino pawl cu Biakinn sung hmanah a that; zovek tlun hmanah zaangfahnak a nei lo; mino siseh, upa siseh, nunau mipa tilo in, a na mi le harhdam mi tla an zatein a kut sungah Bawipa in a pek ṭheh a si.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Babilon siangpahrang in Bawipa ih Biakinn a siim ih thilri le sumsaw, siangpahrang le a kuthnuai bawi pawl thilri mankhung hmuahhmuah a lak ih Babilon ah a phur ṭheh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Jerusalem khawpi le Bawipa Biakinn, siangpahrang innpi le a sung thilri pawl tla meisa in a ur ṭheh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ralnam in thah ngah lomi, a taanglai mi pawl cu Babilon ah a hruai thluh ih cutawkah, Persia uknak a thlen hlan lo, Babilon siangpahrang le a tesinfa pawl ih sal ah an cang.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cuticun profet Jeremiah hmangin Bawipa ih a rak simmi, “An ulh lomi Sabbath colhnak  kimter dingah an ram cu kum sawmsarih sung a ṭhing ding,” a timi thu cu a kim a si.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Persia siangpahrang Sairas in siangpahrang a ṭuan kum khatnak ah Bawipa ih fial vekin ca a ngan ih a uk sung khuazakipih siar ding in a kuat. Himi cu profet Jeremiah hmangin Bawipa ih thusimmi kimnakah a si. A thusuahmi cu hiti in a ngan:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Himi cu Persia siangpahrang Sairas thusuah mi a si. Bawipa vanih Pathian in leilung pumpuluk uktu ah i tuah ih Judah ram Jerusalem khua ah amah hrangih Biakinn sak dingah ṭuanvo i pek. Cu a si ruangah nannih Pathian minung hmuahhmuah cutawkah feh thluh uh; Bawipa nan Pathian cu nan hnenah um hram seh,” tiah a ngan."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;